NK010(tha)016:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las smad las spu gri rlung
NK010(tha)016:1: 'khor zhes bya ba ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa
NK010(tha)016:2: man ngag ltar bkral ba chig brgyud ma /
NK010(tha)016:7: na mahsh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra ya /
NK010(tha)016:8: lnga brgya tha ma'i yang mtha' 'dir //
NK010(tha)016:9: rgyal bstan ri mo'i mar me yang //
NK010(tha)016:10: nyams pa bdun gyis bsub pa'i dus //
NK010(tha)016:11: drag sngags rgyal po'i grub mtha' bslang //
NK010(tha)016:12: bstan 'gro'i don la ma yin par //
NK010(tha)016:13: gzhan 'byor dpal la mi bzod pas //
NK010(tha)016:14: rang gar spyod na phur srung gis //
NK010(tha)016:15: de yi don snying lkog mar phyung //
NK010(tha)016:21: rdo rje gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK010(tha)016:22: phur pa rgyud kyi rgyal po yin //
NK010(tha)016:23: phur pa lung gi bla ma yin //
NK010(tha)016:24: phur pa man ngag nges pa'i don //
NK010(tha)016:25: zhes rgyud lung man ngag gsum gyi bshad thabs yod pa las /
NK010(tha)016:26: 'dir rgyud kyi dgongs pa gtso bor byas nas lung dang man ngag gis bkral ba la /
NK010(tha)016:28: stong pa nyid dang snying rje gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems yin te /
NK010(tha)016:29: byams pa chen po'i byin rlabs las //
NK010(tha)016:30: chos nyid phur pa cir yang snang //
NK010(tha)016:31: rdo rje phur pa'i ngo bo ste //
NK010(tha)016:34: phur ni thams cad byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)016:35: pa ni thams cad kun tu khyab //
NK010(tha)016:36: phur ni thams cad gtso bo mchog /
NK010(tha)016:37: pa ni thams cad 'khor gyi tshul //
NK010(tha)016:38: phur ni thams cad skye ba med //
NK010(tha)016:39: pa ni rol pa 'gag pa med //
NK010(tha)016:40: phur ni byang chub sems su gcig /
NK010(tha)016:41: pa ni thams cad de ru bsgrub //
NK010(tha)016:44: phur pa rnam pa bzhi yin te //
NK010(tha)016:45: chos nyid don gyi phur pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:46: rig pa ye shes phur pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:47: 'dus byas rdzas kyi phur pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:48: brten pa lus kyi phur pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:51: rang rig ye shes phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:52: gdab yul chos kyi dbyings nyid dang //
NK010(tha)016:53: thugs rje chen po'i phur pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:54: khams gsum sems can la gdab dang //
NK010(tha)016:55: gsang ba byang sems phur pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:56: yum gyi mkha' la gdab pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:57: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:58: nyams pa bdun la gdab pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:60: de la 'dir smad las kyi ngo bo ngan sngags
NK010(tha)016:61: nye bar bsnyen pa ni 'dus byas rdzas kyi phur
NK010(tha)016:62: pa la brten nas bsgrub pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)016:63: 'dus byas rdzas kyi phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:64: bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur la gdab //
NK010(tha)016:65: man ngag nyid du bkol ba bdun //
NK010(tha)016:66: med du mi rung de bzhin bshams //
NK010(tha)016:67: bsnyen phur la yang rnam pa gnyis //
NK010(tha)016:68: nyung dkar dang ni phur bu dngos //
NK010(tha)016:69: lcags sna lnga'am bdun kyang rung //
NK010(tha)016:70: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur gsum //
NK010(tha)016:71: sked pa rgya mdud gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)016:72: lcum gzhogs la ni sor bcu gnyis //
NK010(tha)016:73: bsnyen pa'i phur pa de bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)016:74: seng ldeng phur pa sor brgyad ni //
NK010(tha)016:75: mthu 'phrog byin rlabs yod pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:76: de bzhin bya rgod gshog phur yang //
NK010(tha)016:77: 'gugs par bya ba'i nus pa yod //
NK010(tha)016:78: ser po gser ram yang na ni //
NK010(tha)016:79: skyer pa dag la byas pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:80: zil gyis gnon pa'i phur pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:81: skyes pa dar ma rigs can gyi //
NK010(tha)016:82: sbom po ma yin thur ma phra mo tsam //
NK010(tha)016:83: zangs sam mdzo mo shing dag gis //
NK010(tha)016:84: dmar po dag la byas pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:85: dbang du 'dus pa'i phur bur bstan //
NK010(tha)016:86: tsan+dana dag gam rgya shug ni //
NK010(tha)016:87: gzi byin 'phrog par yang dag bstan //
NK010(tha)016:88: lcags sam shing ni nag po'am //
NK010(tha)016:89: drag por gyur pa mtha' dag la //
NK010(tha)016:90: rdul du brlag par rab tu bstan //
NK010(tha)016:92: khyad par sras phur gyi rgyu lcags sna lnga ni myang 'das las /
NK010(tha)016:93: gnam lcags sa 'di sa mad'i lde'u sogs sngon chad
NK010(tha)016:94: rtags phyin pa'i lde'u yin par gsang dgongs las bshad
NK010(tha)016:95: cing gzhan du lha khang rnying pa'i sgo gzer kyang
NK010(tha)016:97: mi rta bsad pa'i mtshon rtse bzhi //
NK010(tha)016:98: phal pa'i lcags dang lnga la bya //
NK010(tha)016:101: gser dngul zangs lcags 'khar ba rnams //
NK010(tha)016:104: de bzhin sher shing rwa mtshon rkang //
NK010(tha)016:105: glang po che dang gcan gzan /
NK010(tha)016:106: gdug pa can dang bkra mi shis //
NK010(tha)016:107: khyo dgu shi ba'i yugs mo'i 'phang //
NK010(tha)016:108: de la drag po'i phur pa bya //
NK010(tha)016:111: rtsa ba'i phyogs su rgya mdud bya //
NK010(tha)016:112: rtse mo rang rang gzhung bzhin gzhog /
NK010(tha)016:114: tshad dang dbyibs dang grangs nges kyi sgo nas bshad na /
NK010(tha)016:115: sor brgyad sor drug bcu gnyis dang //
NK010(tha)016:116: bcu drug phur pa'i tshad yin no //
NK010(tha)016:117: zlum dang gru bzhi zla gam dang //
NK010(tha)016:118: zur gsum dbyibs su nges pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:119: gcig dang lha grangs mnyam pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:120: zhes pas las bzhi'i khyad par nges par byas shing /
NK010(tha)016:121: de yang shing gcig nas bzo na /
NK010(tha)016:122: zhi rtse rgyas pa rtsa ba dbang //
NK010(tha)016:123: drag po sa yi gting la bya //
NK010(tha)016:125: tshad kyi khyad par zhib pa ni rdo rje khros pa'i bshad rgyud las /
NK010(tha)016:126: shing lcags gnyis kyi tshad dang dbyibs //
NK010(tha)016:127: sor brgyad tshad du rdzogs pa la //
NK010(tha)016:128: dbu yi rgya mdud sor gcig ste //
NK010(tha)016:129: zur gsum brgyad dang gru bzhi lnga //
NK010(tha)016:130: h+aum mdzad khrag 'thung lnga rdzogs te //
NK010(tha)016:131: sor gnyis lte ba yan chad la //
NK010(tha)016:132: lcum gzhogs brgyad du yang dag shes //
NK010(tha)016:133: khro rgyal mgo brnyan bcu drug rdzogs //
NK010(tha)016:134: sor gcig lte ba gsus pa de //
NK010(tha)016:135: sgo bzhi sgo ma bzhi dang ldan //
NK010(tha)016:136: 'og gi stobs chen de nyid do //
NK010(tha)016:137: sor gcig btsos po mtshan ma ste //
NK010(tha)016:138: chu srin kha ru yang dag rdzogs //
NK010(tha)016:140: sor gsum dbal dang ldan pa ste //
NK010(tha)016:141: yum chen lnga yi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK010(tha)016:142: bcu gnyis ldan na dbus de gtso //
NK010(tha)016:143: sor re yin zhing sku stod la //
NK010(tha)016:144: sor gsum ldan pa rdzogs par bya //
NK010(tha)016:145: gzhan drug dbal du shes par bya //
NK010(tha)016:146: sor drug brgyad 'dra chung ba nyid //
NK010(tha)016:147: sor ni bcu drug ldan pa la //
NK010(tha)016:148: sor gnyis dbu yin sku stod bzhi //
NK010(tha)016:149: lte ba gnyis la mtshan ma gnyis //
NK010(tha)016:150: drug ni dbal du rdzogs pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:151: cha tshad ldan pas rtags myur ro //
NK010(tha)016:152: rab gnas rtse gcig yid kyis rdzogs //
NK010(tha)016:153: rang gi lus nyid phur pa ste //
NK010(tha)016:154: mgo bo rgya mdud gong ma yin //
NK010(tha)016:155: sku stod lcum gzhogs brgyad yin la //
NK010(tha)016:156: lte ba rgya mdud 'og ma yin //
NK010(tha)016:157: btsos po mtshan ma chu srin kha //
NK010(tha)016:158: rkang pa gnyis ni dbal du shes //
NK010(tha)016:159: lus kyi nang du lha rdzogs pas //
NK010(tha)016:160: phur pa gcig tu bsgrub pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:161: las rnams 'grub par the tshom med //
NK010(tha)016:162: tshon sna lnga'am ba su ta'i //
NK010(tha)016:163: gzungs thag ldan pa bzlas pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:164: bye ba gcig gis lding bar 'gyur //
NK010(tha)016:166: de yis las rnams thams cad 'grub //
NK010(tha)016:168: de'ang gsang ba'i dgongs rgyud sogs las ring tshad sor bco brgyad dang /
NK010(tha)016:169: thung tshad sor bzhir bshad nas /
NK010(tha)016:170: de las thung bar ma gsungs so //
NK010(tha)016:171: de las ring bar yongs ma gsungs //
NK010(tha)016:172: zhes bshad pa'i dag pa ni /
NK010(tha)016:178: khams bco brgyad gnas su dag pa'i don dang sbyor na /
NK010(tha)016:179: chos nyid kyi phur pa nas gang ba re zhig
NK010(tha)016:180: ting 'dzin sems dpa' la dmigs par go na legs
NK010(tha)016:181: te / gzhan du rdo rje bkod pa las kyang /
NK010(tha)016:182: de la chos nyid kyi phur pa ni /
NK010(tha)016:183: chos can gang la'ang mi dmigs so //
NK010(tha)016:185: de lta bu'i phur pa 'du byed pa'i gang zag kyang /
NK010(tha)016:186: dge slong shan pa dge bsnyen dang //
NK010(tha)016:188: lha bzos blangs pa mchog yin no //
NK010(tha)016:189: zhe gnag khrims gtsang sdom ldan pa //
NK010(tha)016:190: dbang thob dad pa ldan pas gzungs //
NK010(tha)016:191: bzo mkhas yon tan ldan pas bya //
NK010(tha)016:193: de ltar rgyu rkyen rten 'brel thams cad tshogs pa'i
NK010(tha)016:194: phur bu ni dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i thugs kyi rten
NK010(tha)016:195: yin pas dngos grub kyi rdzas su gzung ba'i tshul
NK010(tha)016:196: / phur pa lha yi dkyil 'khor kyang /
NK010(tha)016:197: thugs kyi rten las yang dag 'grub //
NK010(tha)016:200: nyal na sngas su bltar mi mngon pa'i tshul gyis 'bral spang bya ba yang /
NK010(tha)016:201: sras mchog phur bu'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)016:202: kun la bstan par mi bya'o //
NK010(tha)016:204: khrag dang gu gul skabs su bdug /
NK010(tha)016:205: sngags ni nyin mtshan sum stong re //
NK010(tha)016:206: dar ram ras kyis dkris la sba //
NK010(tha)016:207: 'bral bar mi bya lus la bcang //
NK010(tha)016:208: btab na lha yang brlag par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)016:209: yongs grub dngos grub myur du thob //
NK010(tha)016:211: de yang smad las kyi skabs 'dir sgrub phur ram /
NK010(tha)016:212: lha phur med na gdab phur nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK010(tha)016:213: ni med du mi rung ba yin pas dkyil 'khor
NK010(tha)016:214: gyi lha gnas so so dang /
NK010(tha)016:216: bdag nyid bsrung ba byad bzlog pa //
NK010(tha)016:217: brub khung gong bzhin mchod rten bca' //
NK010(tha)016:218: dam rdzas tshang bar nges pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:219: lha phur rangs po kun la yang //
NK010(tha)016:220: sngags pas bsrung bzlog btags la bri //
NK010(tha)016:221: bum pa dag la dgod par bya //
NK010(tha)016:222: 'og tu gsad pa'i rim pa bya //
NK010(tha)016:223: zhes rnal 'byor chen po las nang 'gras la sogs
NK010(tha)016:224: pa'i bsrung bzlog dmigs bsal gyi mchod rten bcas chog
NK010(tha)016:225: kyang yod de / 'dir lha phur lha gnas dang gdab phur thod par sbams pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)016:226: mtshan dang ldan pa'i b+han+d+ha ru //
NK010(tha)016:227: nag po 'bru yis bkang nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:228: rim par bzhugs shing byin brlab bya //
NK010(tha)016:229: mthing nag dar gyis kha bcad la //
NK010(tha)016:230: byin brlab dbang bskur gzhung bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)016:231: mi 'gyur pho brang rdzas su dgod //
NK010(tha)016:234: yal ga med pa'i b+han+d+ha ni //
NK010(tha)016:235: thod pa rab tu legs pa la //
NK010(tha)016:236: yugs sa mo yi mngal khrag gis //
NK010(tha)016:238: phrin las bzhi yi dbyibs bya'o //
NK010(tha)016:239: de la dgra bgegs ming byang gzhug /
NK010(tha)016:240: bsnyen pa'i phur pas gzir la bzhag /
NK010(tha)016:242: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gsum las /
NK010(tha)016:244: de nas drag po'i las bya ba //
NK010(tha)016:246: phur pa drug bcas rab bkod de //
NK010(tha)016:247: ling+ga thun rdzas drag po'i rdzas //
NK010(tha)016:248: gsang sngags rdzas su shes par bya //
NK010(tha)016:250: lcags phur dbus su dgod par bya //
NK010(tha)016:251: mi bzad phur pa drug rnams ni //
NK010(tha)016:252: gru gsum drug la shes par bya //
NK010(tha)016:253: zhes pa la sogs pa'i don zhib pa ni dam
NK010(tha)016:254: can nye bar bsnyen pa dang 'brel na de'i man
NK010(tha)016:255: ngag dang bstun nas rang lugs btsan par bya /
NK010(tha)016:256: las drug khol bton gyi tshe /
NK010(tha)016:257: dkyil 'khor gyi stegs bu'i 'og tu bye stegs zur
NK010(tha)016:258: gsum pa'i dbus gsad dkyil rgyar khru gang zabs khru
NK010(tha)016:259: phyed pa can gru gsum du brus par phung sa
NK010(tha)016:260: dang ro sol gyis nag por bya /
NK010(tha)016:261: logs gsum du mda' gzhu bkang ba re dang /
NK010(tha)016:262: zur gsum la za byed zhal re bri /
NK010(tha)016:263: de'i kha khyer rtsibs drug tu byas pa las sras
NK010(tha)016:264: mchog ngo bo mi bzad pa'i phur pa drug dang
NK010(tha)016:265: / mtha' la dam can gyi snam bu la phur
NK010(tha)016:266: pa bcu gnyis sam yang na shar nas brtsams dam
NK010(tha)016:267: can gyi phur pa gsum dang byang du ming po'i
NK010(tha)016:268: / phur pa bkod / nya bo'i rgyu ni /
NK010(tha)016:269: grog mkhar sa dang mi phung sa //
NK010(tha)016:271: gangs kyi dum bu ju tse'i phub //
NK010(tha)016:272: srub ka'i lo ma zhing chen ras //
NK010(tha)016:273: ske tshe dang ni ldong ros dang //
NK010(tha)016:274: thal chen dang ni rak+ta dang //
NK010(tha)016:275: bshang ba dang ni gci ba ste //
NK010(tha)016:276: bcu gnyis thod pa nang du blugs //
NK010(tha)016:277: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)016:278: mut+ka ra a ko ta ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:279: ra thug lug thug gcin gyis sbru //
NK010(tha)016:280: zhes pa ltar las grog mkhar ni rgya grog dmar po dang /
NK010(tha)016:282: rgya mtsho'i 'gram mam chu klung chen po'i 'gram sa /
NK010(tha)016:287: dri ma drug la sogs pa'ang 'dres par byas nas
NK010(tha)016:288: nya bo sor bcu gnyis pa byas pa'i srog pa
NK010(tha)016:289: rtsa'i dod du dur khrod kyi r+ts+wa ku sha bcug
NK010(tha)016:290: cing / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya pa sham bi sho d+ha bam kham h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:291: n+ri tri m+aa ra ya phata /
NK010(tha)016:293: yang ling+ga ris su 'bri na gang zag zhe sdang
NK010(tha)016:294: can sngags kyi theg pa la dad cing mdog nag
NK010(tha)016:296: smin mtshams su khro gnyer gsum pa mche ba can /
NK010(tha)016:297: chu bya'i lag can gyis smin drug sa 'og tu
NK010(tha)016:298: song ba'i dus btsal ba'i smyug gu kang+ka la sogs
NK010(tha)016:301: dpyid zla 'bring po lha mo u ma'i gsang bar
NK010(tha)016:302: zla gsang dkar dmar 'char ba'i dus btsal ba'i snag
NK010(tha)016:303: tsha ni ma pa'i khu ba dang bsres pa nye
NK010(tha)016:304: bar bsdogs shing nyi nag la bab pa'i tshe /
NK010(tha)016:305: gong gi rgyu de dag gis sbags pa'i gro ga'am /
NK010(tha)016:306: zhing ras la sogs par ling+ga mtshan nyid tshang bar
NK010(tha)016:307: bris pa'i snying gar khrag chen gyis h+aum che ge
NK010(tha)016:308: mo m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:310: nya bo yin na bzhi snying dril bas mgo bsnan te bris pa snying gar slan /
NK010(tha)016:311: gnyis ka la dpral ba klad rgyas 'khor lo la
NK010(tha)016:312: sogs pa drug man ngag ltar bri ma nus na
NK010(tha)016:313: / spyi bor lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nan dang /
NK010(tha)016:314: dpral bar che ge mo ha sa ya ra hri ta na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:320: gsang gnas rnams la sngags drug po ming spel can bkod /
NK010(tha)016:321: gegs kyi r+au pa yin na ming bzhi 'dus pa'i
NK010(tha)016:322: phung po'i rten 'brel las sngags drug po rim pa
NK010(tha)016:327: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po bzhi /
NK010(tha)016:328: so rnams la bri ba man ngag yin no //
NK010(tha)016:329: ling+ga'i mtha' la bzhi snying dril ba dmod pa dang bcas pa /
NK010(tha)016:330: de'i mthar dza khrmo gyis bskor /
NK010(tha)016:331: d+ha du ra la sogs pa'i dug khrag byug /
NK010(tha)016:333: tshon skud sna lngas cung zad dkris la phung thod dum drug gam /
NK010(tha)016:335: mon nag la sogs pa'i thod par bcug /
NK010(tha)016:336: bsnyen phur gyis gzir nas bzhag pa gsad dkyil du 'jug pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)016:337: dbus su brub khung thur du bru //
NK010(tha)016:338: de nas thod par ling+ga bca' //
NK010(tha)016:341: nyung dkar nyung nag ske tshe dang //
NK010(tha)016:342: shang tshe phyi ma gsum dang ldan //
NK010(tha)016:343: rdo dreg zi ra til nag dang //
NK010(tha)016:344: dug khrag tshogs pas rno ngar bskyed //
NK010(tha)016:346: dam can so so'i thun rdzas ni //
NK010(tha)016:347: nyug dkar la sogs rdzas bzhi la //
NK010(tha)016:348: bse mo'i sngags dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK010(tha)016:349: rim gyi phyi mo la sogs bzhi //
NK010(tha)016:350: bdag nyid ma yi sngags dang ni //
NK010(tha)016:351: lcags phye la sogs rdzas bzhi la //
NK010(tha)016:352: shwa na'i sngags dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK010(tha)016:353: tshig bzhis bden pa bdar la dbab //
NK010(tha)016:355: gnyis pa cho ga'i gzhung bsrang ba la gsum /
NK010(tha)016:356: rtsa ba dkyus su bsdeb pa dang /
NK010(tha)016:357: dkyus khong khrar gtang ba dang /
NK010(tha)016:358: dngos grub blang ba'i khyad par gnyis bstan pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:361: dang po ting 'dzin rnam gsum nas //
NK010(tha)016:362: rdzogs pas mthing nag 'bar ba ste //
NK010(tha)016:363: de la mchod bstod rdzogs par bya //
NK010(tha)016:364: 'khor lo drug la dregs pa drug /
NK010(tha)016:365: khyams la ma bdun srung ma gsum //
NK010(tha)016:366: rim par rdzogs tshul shes par bya //
NK010(tha)016:367: mchod pa bstod pa yan chad bya //
NK010(tha)016:368: dang po gtso bo'i gsang sngags dang //
NK010(tha)016:369: ming rus bcas pa'i nges pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:370: ha sa ya ra'i yi ge dgu //
NK010(tha)016:371: sum brgya drug bcu'i gtso bo ste //
NK010(tha)016:372: dgra lha'i rgyal po'i snying po yin //
NK010(tha)016:373: dang po zhag gcig lha dang dbral //
NK010(tha)016:374: de nas srung ma ma bdun sngags //
NK010(tha)016:375: thun dang bcas pas gsad par bya //
NK010(tha)016:376: rtsa bas dam can gnad la dbab //
NK010(tha)016:377: +aa be sha yi yi ge bcu //
NK010(tha)016:378: klu yi rgyal po'i gsang sngags yin //
NK010(tha)016:379: nub gnyis gzugs la dbab pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:380: shi kri a na'i yi ge bdun //
NK010(tha)016:381: khu le lag dgu'i gsang sngags te //
NK010(tha)016:382: gsum pa byad du gzhug pa'o //

NK010(tha)016:748: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlogs //
NK010(tha)016:750: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya /
NK010(tha)016:752: rdo rje tho bas rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)016:755: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i thugs ka nas //
NK010(tha)016:756: pho nya tho ba can dag ni //
NK010(tha)016:757: grangs med 'od zer bcas pa byung //
NK010(tha)016:758: gzas po'i gzugs kyi phung po ni //
NK010(tha)016:759: ma lus rdul du brlag par bsam //
NK010(tha)016:766: dam nyams pa'i dgra bo che ge mo'i gzugs phung
NK010(tha)016:767: skye mched dang bcas pa 'bar ba chen po'i tho
NK010(tha)016:768: gtun gyi bar du rdul du rlog cig /
NK010(tha)016:769: bsdus 'joms bzhin du brdungs nas sha myog rus myog tu thong zhig /
NK010(tha)016:771: tshe'i gnad gcod pa lcags phur snying dkar nag mtshams su btab nas /
NK010(tha)016:773: zhes pas sems kyi dpyis 'byin no //
NK010(tha)016:774: drug pa zhal du bstab pa'i las la drug las /
NK010(tha)016:775: dang po las drug gi dkyus ltar ting nge 'dzin gyis bstab pa'i bskul ni /
NK010(tha)016:777: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:778: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:779: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:780: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:781: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:782: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:784: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:785: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:786: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)016:787: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)016:788: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)016:789: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par byos //
NK010(tha)016:790: zhal du bstab bo kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK010(tha)016:791: sku yi gzi brjid rgyas par mdzod //
NK010(tha)016:793: bin+d+ha ya ban+d+hi ya bzhi pa rdzas ni /
NK010(tha)016:794: bstab pa hom gzar rgya yis bya //
NK010(tha)016:797: 'od zer sprul pa grangs med kyis //
NK010(tha)016:798: gzas po'i dbang po 'du ba dang //
NK010(tha)016:799: sha khrag rus chen rgyu ma gzir //
NK010(tha)016:800: bstab pas rol par de bzhin bsam //
NK010(tha)016:803: lag gnyis hom gzar gyi rgya dang bcas /
NK010(tha)016:806: dam nyams pa'i dgra bo che ge mo'i phung khams
NK010(tha)016:807: skye mched bsod nams za thang dang bcas pa rjes
NK010(tha)016:808: shul tsam yang med par zhal du thob cig /
NK010(tha)016:813: bkrag mdangs kyi gnad gcod skyer phur lte bar btab la /
NK010(tha)016:814: su ru su ru u tsush+ma ma h+aa kro ta m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:815: ces bzlas pas lte ba srid pa skyed byed gzhom mo //
NK010(tha)016:816: de ltar gsang ba'i tshig drug gis bskul zhing gab pa'i sngags drug khong khrar gtang ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:817: bsad las kyi ngo bo nyid yin te /
NK010(tha)016:819: sngon gyi dus gsang ba'i tshig drug po 'di de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis kyang ma gsungs pas /
NK010(tha)016:820: las kyi sems dpa' yang skrag nas sa la 'gyel
NK010(tha)016:821: zhing 'jig rten cher g.yos shing rab tu g.yos par
NK010(tha)016:823: gnyis pa las drug char gyi khong khrag gtang ba gdab las la don drug las /
NK010(tha)016:826: drug rdzogs phur pas gdab pa yang //
NK010(tha)016:827: bsnyen phur btab la tshe lung bya //
NK010(tha)016:829: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad kyi gnad gcod cing /
NK010(tha)016:830: khams dang skye mched kyi nyer len dag par byed
NK010(tha)016:831: pa ni phur bu nyer lnga'i gdab las yin la
NK010(tha)016:832: / rnam dbye'i ngos nas nyams pa bdun la gdab
NK010(tha)016:833: pa'i mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa byug bdug brab
NK010(tha)016:834: gsum la brten nas gzi byin bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)016:836: gu gul bdug cing nyung kar brdeg /
NK010(tha)016:837: ra khyi'i khrag dang gsur chen gyi //
NK010(tha)016:838: so so'i snying po gdon zhing byug /
NK010(tha)016:839: dbang bskur byin rlabs mchog tu gsungs //
NK010(tha)016:841: ma gu ta la pra ta /
NK010(tha)016:842: sogs sgrub thabs nang ltar bazla'o //
NK010(tha)016:843: gnyis pa bsnyen phur bdag nyid chen po'i rang bzhin du dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK010(tha)016:845: lag pa g.yas pa'i steng du ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:846: g.yon par a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du a /
NK010(tha)016:847: g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du gung mo la /
NK010(tha)016:850: srin lag la h+r+aih mthe chung la +aa bsam /
NK010(tha)016:851: g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du gung mo la m+aum /
NK010(tha)016:856: de nas su ra s+t+wam zhes rdo rje thal mo mnyam par sbyar /
NK010(tha)016:857: badz+ra any+dza li h+aum zhes sor mo cung zad bsnol /
NK010(tha)016:858: badz+ra b+han+d+ha bam zhes sor mo rgyab sbyar nas bsdam /
NK010(tha)016:859: sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes phur pa blangs te chang
NK010(tha)016:860: par bcug lag pa'i rting pa phye ste mthe bong
NK010(tha)016:862: mathe'u chung gi dbrag tu bcug la /
NK010(tha)016:863: mthe bong bsgul zhing bsgril nas badz+ra +aa be sha ya a /
NK010(tha)016:865: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa yab yum sras dang
NK010(tha)016:866: bcas pa thams cad zhe sdang rjes su dran pa'i
NK010(tha)016:867: sku nyung 'bru tsam grangs med pa bsdus shing bstim
NK010(tha)016:869: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK010(tha)016:870: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)016:871: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs bya'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:872: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsol cig /
NK010(tha)016:873: +amo h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah +aa be sha ya /
NK010(tha)016:876: sor mo bcu khro bcur mos pa'i bar du dril nas bsnyen phur byin gyis brlabs /
NK010(tha)016:877: de yang skabs 'di dag tu phur pa'i phyag rgya lnga ni /
NK010(tha)016:879: phur pa'i phyag rgya lnga ru bshad //
NK010(tha)016:880: phur pa dam tshig phyag rgya ste //
NK010(tha)016:881: lag pa gnyis kyi rting sbyar nas //
NK010(tha)016:882: gung mo rtse sprad bar du bsgril //
NK010(tha)016:883: 'di ni phur bu'i dam tshig rgya //
NK010(tha)016:885: tshangs pas sor brgyad rim pas gzung //
NK010(tha)016:886: lhag ma rtse mo mnan chad pa //
NK010(tha)016:887: phur pa brdeg pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK010(tha)016:888: lag pa gnyis ni thal sbyar nas //
NK010(tha)016:889: gung mo rtse sprad mathe'u chung brkyang //
NK010(tha)016:890: srin lag mdzub mo rgyab bsnol te //
NK010(tha)016:891: mthe bong gshib ste bar du bsgril //
NK010(tha)016:892: 'di ni phur pa bsgril ba'i rgya //
NK010(tha)016:893: ha na ha na d+aip+ta tsakra h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:894: lag pa gnyis kyi rting sprad nas //
NK010(tha)016:895: sor bcu khro bcur byin brlabs te //
NK010(tha)016:896: sras mchog dkyil du bzhag nas kyang //
NK010(tha)016:897: byin gyis brlab par byas pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:898: phur pa byin gyis rlob pa'i rgya //
NK010(tha)016:899: h+r+aihb+hu ba b+hu ba h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:900: mtheb mdzub gnyis kyi bar du ni //
NK010(tha)016:901: phur pa bcug la yar 'phangs nas //
NK010(tha)016:902: babs pa brdeg pa'i gzugs la bsnun //
NK010(tha)016:903: 'di ni phur pa bskul ba'i rgya //
NK010(tha)016:904: don du phyag rgya la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)016:905: yang dag rtogs na kun kyang rgya //
NK010(tha)016:906: ma rtogs mtshan ma rtog pa'i zhing //
NK010(tha)016:908: byin gyis brlab pa'i rgyas phur pa gyen du gsor zhing /
NK010(tha)016:910: srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:911: dbang dang dngos grub stsol ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:912: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK010(tha)016:913: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)016:914: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:915: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:916: zhes rdo rje'i tshig drug gi mgo bsnan nas /
NK010(tha)016:917: h+aum bzhi gsal 'phro h+aum bzhi tshogs las bskyed //
NK010(tha)016:918: dbu la rgya mdud bstan pas thabs kyi rtags //
NK010(tha)016:919: rtsibs la logs brgyad bstan pas khro bo brgyad //
NK010(tha)016:920: rin chen zur brgyad bstan pas khro mo brgyad //
NK010(tha)016:921: dbus su rgya mdud bstan pas shes rab rtags //
NK010(tha)016:922: rtse mo zur gsum bstan pas sku gsung thugs //
NK010(tha)016:923: steng 'og gnyis su bstan pas khro bo gnyis //
NK010(tha)016:924: khong stong byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)016:925: khro rgyal 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)016:926: ma g.yos chos mchog sku gsung thugs kyi bdag /
NK010(tha)016:927: sdug bsngal log par 'khyams pa'i sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)016:928: thugs rje gnyis med dbyings su sgrol mdzad pas //
NK010(tha)016:929: thabs kyis bsgral ba'i skal ba mi ldan yang //
NK010(tha)016:930: shugs kyis bsgral ba'i phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:931: zhes bskul la log rdugs 'byams gsum phyi nyes pa sel zhing /
NK010(tha)016:932: sgrol ba rang rgyud pa ldog phyir bdag nyid dpal chen po /
NK010(tha)016:933: zhe sdang rang rgyud pa ldog phyir bsnyen phur sras mchog /
NK010(tha)016:934: gzhan don yal bar mi dor bas nya bo dmigs
NK010(tha)016:935: bya dngos te gsal ba gsum ldan gyi rang bzhin
NK010(tha)016:936: stong nyid snying rjer shar ba'i thugs rje chen po'i
NK010(tha)016:937: phur pas log 'dren tshar gcod pa sngags lam thabs
NK010(tha)016:938: la mkhas pa'i sgrol ba ste /
NK010(tha)016:940: thog mar rtogs goms bdag nyid bsgral //
NK010(tha)016:941: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK010(tha)016:942: blo ngan sems can yun du 'khor //
NK010(tha)016:943: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK010(tha)016:945: de la khrus lung gi dgongs pas dmigs bya'i las nyon sbyang ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:946: dgongs pa ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK010(tha)016:947: khrus lung nyon mongs dag byas shing //
NK010(tha)016:949: sras mchog gi spyi bor h+aum mdzad dang /
NK010(tha)016:950: h+aum mdzad kyi spyi bor a dkar po gcig bsam pa 'od du zhu nas h+aum mdzad la thim /
NK010(tha)016:951: h+aum mdzad sras mchog la thim pa'i rkyen gyis gzi byin mchog tu 'bar /
NK010(tha)016:952: de'i 'od zer gyis dmigs bya'i las nyon sbyang bar bsams la /
NK010(tha)016:953: sras mchog gi phur pa dam tshig gi rgyas bzung
NK010(tha)016:954: ba snying gar ma reg tsam du lan gsum bsgril
NK010(tha)016:956: byams dang snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)016:957: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK010(tha)016:958: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK010(tha)016:959: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK010(tha)016:960: lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha nan /
NK010(tha)016:961: mo ha g+ha ya b+ha ga w+aa na shi kri bi kri /
NK010(tha)016:962: sh+ri badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:964: yab yum thabs shes su sbyor ba'i thabs kyis ming
NK010(tha)016:965: rus tshogs pa'i rten gyi bag chags sbyong zhing stong
NK010(tha)016:966: pa chen po sgrol ba'i shes rab kyis las dang
NK010(tha)016:967: bag chags kyi mthus bskyed pa'i rnam smin gyi cha
NK010(tha)016:968: lhag ma med par sbyong ba'i sngags don dran par
NK010(tha)016:969: bya ba ni snying po sngags kyi khrus lung ste
NK010(tha)016:970: / lam h+aum lam yab dang yum //
NK010(tha)016:971: s+t+wam b+ha thabs dang shes rab sngags //
NK010(tha)016:972: gnyis med sbyor bas nyon mongs sbyongs //
NK010(tha)016:973: drag po yab yum sgrol bar bshad //
NK010(tha)016:974: mo ha ming la g+ha ya rus //
NK010(tha)016:975: rten la dbab pa'i las su bshad //
NK010(tha)016:976: b+ha ga w+aan ni bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)016:977: sgrol ba'i gtso bo yin par bshad //
NK010(tha)016:978: shi kri yab dang bi kri yum //
NK010(tha)016:979: gnyis med yab yum byang du bshad //
NK010(tha)016:980: badz+ra h+aum dang k+aar bcas pa //
NK010(tha)016:981: yang dag don gyi 'bras bu ste //
NK010(tha)016:982: stong pa chen po'i sgrol bar bshad //
NK010(tha)016:984: de nas sku phyag rgya chen po'i khrus lung dang
NK010(tha)016:985: 'brel bar rang rig ye shes kyi phur pa chos
NK010(tha)016:986: kyi dbyings su gdab pas gnas spar ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:987: tshe srog dbang sdud sgrol ba yi //
NK010(tha)016:988: rdo rje phur pa rab btab nas //
NK010(tha)016:989: srid pa'i tshe dang phral nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:990: rnam shes rdo rje gzhon nur spar //
NK010(tha)016:992: phur pa dam rgyas bzung bzhin pa las /
NK010(tha)016:993: bdag nyid dpal chen po'i thugs srog las 'od zer 'phros /
NK010(tha)016:994: kho'i snying nang na rnam par shes pa'i rten bla
NK010(tha)016:995: tshe'i ngo bo yi ge n+ri gcig gnas pa phur
NK010(tha)016:996: rtses bshigs nas ar gyur pa bdag gi snying gar
NK010(tha)016:997: gtad pas bla tshe'i snon mar thob par bsam pa
NK010(tha)016:998: la tshe lung zhes kyang bya ste /
NK010(tha)016:999: sran tsam 'od nag dkyil du ni //
NK010(tha)016:1000: khrag gi n+ri ni til 'bru tsam //
NK010(tha)016:1001: gnas pa de ru kun khyab pas //
NK010(tha)016:1002: kun la de bzhin dmigs la gdab //
NK010(tha)016:1004: de nas phur pa bskul ba'i rgyas /
NK010(tha)016:1006: snang srid thams cad phur pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)016:1007: khams gsum 'khor ba ming yang mi grags kyang //
NK010(tha)016:1008: rgyal ba'i rdzu 'phrul chen po bstan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:1009: rdo rje mngon spyod phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1010: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hohsarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:1011: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum h+aum phata phata /
NK010(tha)016:1013: snying gar phur pa bsgril ba'i rgya dang bcas /
NK010(tha)016:1014: ha na ha na d+aip+ta tsakra h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:1015: ces bzla zhing bsgril bas kho'i tshogs drug 'gyu ba'i sgo bkag /
NK010(tha)016:1016: sems dang sems byung gi rgyun bcad /
NK010(tha)016:1017: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa de nyid a dkar po'i rnam par gsal /
NK010(tha)016:1018: de nyid gnas spar ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:1019: phur pa'i rtse mo la'ang a dkar po 'od zer
NK010(tha)016:1020: 'phro ba gsal ba de a'i sgra drag por grags
NK010(tha)016:1021: pa las / kho'i rnam shes kyi ngo bo a
NK010(tha)016:1022: de nyid phur rtse'i a la rtsen gyi 'dus par
NK010(tha)016:1024: thams cad a dkar byang chub sems su gyur //
NK010(tha)016:1025: bsdus pas gser dngul zhi gar blugs pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)016:1026: phur pa'i rtse mo a ni gnas len des //
NK010(tha)016:1027: khab len rdo la lcags rnams 'dus pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)016:1028: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dkar la 'tsher //
NK010(tha)016:1029: sku gsung thugs kyi gnas su bstim par bya //
NK010(tha)016:1030: snang srid tshe bcud tshe yi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1031: khams gsum 'khor ba'i bag chags gdar sha gcad //
NK010(tha)016:1032: nyon mongs 'khor ba thams cad dbyings su bsgral //
NK010(tha)016:1033: rdo rje phur pa skye shi rtsad nas gcod //
NK010(tha)016:1034: badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum a a /
NK010(tha)016:1035: zhes bzla zhing rang gi snying gar phur rtse gtad pas /
NK010(tha)016:1036: phur rtse'i a yang bdag nyid kyi thugs srog la 'dres pas bkrag dang gzi mdangs rgyas /
NK010(tha)016:1037: bdag dang bsgral bya'i rig pa ye shes kyi de
NK010(tha)016:1038: kho na nyid rang bzhin med par rtogs pa'i bden
NK010(tha)016:1039: pas kho yang 'tshengs shing bdag la'ang rnam smin gyis
NK010(tha)016:1042: kun gzhi'i nyon mongs ar gsal bya //
NK010(tha)016:1043: a de bdag la rab bstim pas //
NK010(tha)016:1044: tshe zhes bya ste dngos grub blang //
NK010(tha)016:1047: rnam shes 'phos shing bde ba thob //
NK010(tha)016:1048: rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs kyi //
NK010(tha)016:1049: dag cing tshe 'dzin sngags su gsungs //
NK010(tha)016:1051: gnad de lta bu mi rig pa'i sngags pas rang rgyud kyi sdom pa rtsa ba gcod cing /
NK010(tha)016:1052: rgyud thams cad kyi gleng gzhi las mos pa'i r+au
NK010(tha)016:1053: tra'i go 'phang la de ma thag son nas mthar
NK010(tha)016:1055: nyams pa bsgral na mngon sangs rgya //
NK010(tha)016:1056: kun la byas na dmyal bar ltung //
NK010(tha)016:1058: da ni gdab pa'i cho ga la man ngag gi
NK010(tha)016:1059: gnad ma shes na drag po mngon spyod kyi phrin
NK010(tha)016:1060: las shan pa'i srog las dang 'dra bas /
NK010(tha)016:1061: thog mar khro bo bcu'i phur pas rnam shes tshogs
NK010(tha)016:1062: brgyad kyi gnad gcad pas kun gzhi la 'khor ba'i
NK010(tha)016:1063: bag chags gsog pa'i rgyun chad /
NK010(tha)016:1064: khro mo bcu'i phur pas srid pa chags byed kyi
NK010(tha)016:1065: rten 'byung ba lnga bshigs pas phung po thogs bcas
NK010(tha)016:1067: sgo ba bzhi'i phur pas lus kyi mtsho bzhi la
NK010(tha)016:1068: btab pas skye gnas bzhi'i sgo dgag pa ste rgyud
NK010(tha)016:1069: las / khro bo yab yum bcu po yis //
NK010(tha)016:1070: gnas bcu dug gsum rtsa nas gcod //
NK010(tha)016:1071: sgo ba bzhi yis mtsho bzhi skem //
NK010(tha)016:1073: de la rgyud kyi gleng gzhi dang bstun nas btab kyang 'gal ba yod pa ma yin te /
NK010(tha)016:1074: gdab yul dang gnyen po ma 'phrod pa mang du
NK010(tha)016:1075: snang bar 'dir ni rgyud kyi dgongs pa ltar gdab
NK010(tha)016:1076: pa'i tshul / bsgrub bya bsgral phyir rnam shes rten //
NK010(tha)016:1077: byung tshor sgo ni dgag phyir gdab //
NK010(tha)016:1079: ha na ha na sogs pa'i sngags bcu'i go rim bstan pa'i de ma thag /
NK010(tha)016:1080: mig gnyis rna ba gnyis dang ni //
NK010(tha)016:1081: sna bug gnyis dang lce la gdab //
NK010(tha)016:1082: mgrin pa snying ga khrag sbal dang //
NK010(tha)016:1083: nyon mongs yid la rab tu gdab //
NK010(tha)016:1085: thog mar 'khor ba'i rang bzhin rnam par shes pa'i
NK010(tha)016:1086: tshogs brgyad kyi rten dang brten pa gdab yul du
NK010(tha)016:1087: byas nas / mi dge bcu gnas gyur gyi ngo
NK010(tha)016:1088: bo ye shes kyi khro bo bcu'i phur pas gdab
NK010(tha)016:1089: pa ni 'gying phur so so ma nor bar brdeg
NK010(tha)016:1092: bdag cag rnal 'byor sgrub pa po //
NK010(tha)016:1093: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK010(tha)016:1094: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung gsob pa'i //
NK010(tha)016:1095: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK010(tha)016:1096: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK010(tha)016:1097: bdud dang bar du gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:1099: khro bo chen pos byin rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)016:1100: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK010(tha)016:1101: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK010(tha)016:1102: lus ngag rdul du bshig nas kyang //
NK010(tha)016:1103: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)016:1105: mig g.yas pa la rnam par rgyal ba gdab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1106: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dza h+aum bam hohha
NK010(tha)016:1107: na ha na badz+ra sarba big nan bam h+aum phata
NK010(tha)016:1108: / g.yon pa la dbyug pa sngon po gdab cing thog mtha' 'dra /
NK010(tha)016:1109: da ha da ha badz+ra sarba big des mig gi rnam shes dang /
NK010(tha)016:1110: de'i nye bar len pa tshar gcod do //
NK010(tha)016:1111: rna ba g.yas pa la gshin rje gshed po gdab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1113: pa tsa pa tsa badz+ra g.yon pa la mi g.yo mgon po gdab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1114: ma th+aa ma th+aa badz+ra des rna ba'i rnam shes dang /
NK010(tha)016:1116: sna bug g.yas la rta mgrin rgyal po gdab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1117: dz+wa la dz+wa la badz+ra g.yon pa gzhan gyis mi thub pa la gdab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1118: su ru su ru badz+ra des sna'i rnam shes dang /
NK010(tha)016:1120: lce la h+aum mdzad gdab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1121: mu ru mu ru badz+ra des lce'i rnam shes kyi gzung 'dzin bcom mo //
NK010(tha)016:1122: mgrin par stobs po che btab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1123: ka tam ka te des yid kyi rnam shes kyi gzung 'dzin bcom mo //
NK010(tha)016:1124: snying gar khams gsum rnam rgyal btab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1125: dza ye ta bi dza ye ta des kun gzhi'i
NK010(tha)016:1126: rnam par shes pa bag la nyal stongs par byed
NK010(tha)016:1127: do // nu ma gnyis la bdud rtsi 'khyil pas gdab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1128: a tsi te a pa ra tsi ti des nyon
NK010(tha)016:1129: mongs pa can gyi yid ma rig pa rten dang
NK010(tha)016:1130: bcas pa'i rgyu 'bras bcom pa la bsgral ba rgyu'i
NK010(tha)016:1131: gtso bor byas pa zhes bya ste /
NK010(tha)016:1132: khro bcus gzir ba bcus sbyong ba //
NK010(tha)016:1133: lus kyi gnas bcur gzir zhing sbyang //
NK010(tha)016:1135: des kun gzhi la las mi gsog pa'i thob bya 'bras bu'i go 'phang la sbyor ba'ang /
NK010(tha)016:1136: rnam shes tshogs brgyad la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)016:1137: bsgral ba gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:1138: rnam rgyal la sogs khro bo bcus //
NK010(tha)016:1139: rags pa'i dngos po bcom nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:1140: 'khor ba bskyed pa'i rgyu spangs nas //
NK010(tha)016:1141: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin du //
NK010(tha)016:1142: rtogs pa mchog gi byang chub nyid //
NK010(tha)016:1144: 'o na stobs po che la sogs pa gsum dam
NK010(tha)016:1145: can gyi sngags su 'ong ba ji ltar yin snyam
NK010(tha)016:1146: na / las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig /
NK010(tha)016:1147: 'khor gang yin pa de yang nga nyid yin te /
NK010(tha)016:1148: nga gang yin pa de 'khor rnams yin par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)016:1149: so so ma yin tha mi dad do //
NK010(tha)016:1150: zhes pa ltar 'dir rtsa dum ltar byas so //
NK010(tha)016:1151: spyir khro bo bcu la rtsa sngags las sngags gnyis
NK010(tha)016:1152: las bshad ma thag pa rnams gnyen po rang bzhin
NK010(tha)016:1153: gyi las sngags yin pas rdo rje khros pa la
NK010(tha)016:1154: kro d+ha kro d+ha sogs gsum po'ang dngos bstan yod
NK010(tha)016:1155: do // de skad du rgyud las /
NK010(tha)016:1156: de bas gnyen po'i sngags 'di yang khro bo bcu rnams kyi las sngags yin par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)016:1158: de nas rnam smin 'dus pa'i phung po lus chags
NK010(tha)016:1159: pa'i gnas bcu khams lnga'i nyer len dang bcas pa
NK010(tha)016:1161: klong lnga'i rang bzhin khro mo bcu'i phur pas rgyud kyi gleng gzhi dang mthun par gdab pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)016:1162: bcom ldan 'das kyi lte ba dang //
NK010(tha)016:1163: thugs ka dpung pa dpyi mig dang //
NK010(tha)016:1164: gtsug tor gsang ba'i lam dang ni //
NK010(tha)016:1165: spyi bo rkang mthil gnas rnams nas //
NK010(tha)016:1166: gsang ba'i snying po 'di byung ngo //
NK010(tha)016:1169: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)016:1171: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams /
NK010(tha)016:1172: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par mdzod //
NK010(tha)016:1174: rdo rje snyems ma'i phur pa lte bar btab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1175: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hohpa ra big tan sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:1177: lus chags pa'i rten dang bral /
NK010(tha)016:1178: ming gzugs kyi nyer len bcom /
NK010(tha)016:1180: rgyud drug gnas su dag pa dpal chen po'i ngo bor gyur par bsam /
NK010(tha)016:1181: sder mos snying gar btab la /
NK010(tha)016:1185: lus rgyas pa'i rten rtsa dang bral /
NK010(tha)016:1186: brten pa rlung sems kyi rgyun gcad /
NK010(tha)016:1188: skye mched bcu gnyis kyi rtsa ba gcad /
NK010(tha)016:1189: zhe sdang dag pas dmyal ba'i sgo bkag /
NK010(tha)016:1190: rnam shes rnam dag rdo rje sems dpar gyur par bsam /
NK010(tha)016:1191: rdo rje dur khrod mas dpung pa g.yas dang /
NK010(tha)016:1192: gtun khung mas g.yon pa btab nas /
NK010(tha)016:1196: ser sna stongs pas yi dwags kyi sgo bkag /
NK010(tha)016:1197: tshor ba rnam par dag pa rin 'byung gi ngo bor bsam mo //
NK010(tha)016:1198: rdo rje gtum mos dpyi g.yas dang /
NK010(tha)016:1199: mda' snyems mas g.yon la btab nas /
NK010(tha)016:1200: g+h+ri ha na g+h+ri ha na bzlas pas /
NK010(tha)016:1201: phung po thogs bcas kyi rten dang bral /
NK010(tha)016:1203: phrag dog stongs pas lha min gyi sgo bkag /
NK010(tha)016:1204: 'du byed rnam par dag pa don grub tu gyur par bsam /
NK010(tha)016:1206: de rgyu sems can gyi dus yin pas so //
NK010(tha)016:1207: ha na ha na bzlas pas /
NK010(tha)016:1208: phung po nying mtshams sbyor ba bdag 'dzin gyi rten dang bral /
NK010(tha)016:1210: chos nyid kyi don la rmongs pa'i gti mug dag /
NK010(tha)016:1211: gzugs med dang dud 'gro'i sgo bkag /
NK010(tha)016:1212: gzugs phung rnam par dag pa rnam par snang mdzad du gyur par bsam /
NK010(tha)016:1213: gsod byed mas gsang bar btab la /
NK010(tha)016:1215: khams 'dus pa cha mnyam pas sred len dang bral /
NK010(tha)016:1216: 'dod pa'i 'dod chags la zhen pas 'khor bar skye ba'i rgyun gcad /
NK010(tha)016:1218: 'du shes rnam par dag pa snang ba mtha' yas su gyur par bsam /
NK010(tha)016:1219: sgra 'byin mas spyi bor btab la /
NK010(tha)016:1220: sarba a na ya bzlas pas /
NK010(tha)016:1221: las dge ba la mngon par 'du byed pa'i bzang rtog bcom /
NK010(tha)016:1222: sangs rgyas la thob tu re ba'i blo dor /
NK010(tha)016:1223: 'khor ba la rtag par blta ba'i mtha' bsal nas
NK010(tha)016:1224: rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes
NK010(tha)016:1226: skyod byed mas rkang mthil du btab nas /
NK010(tha)016:1227: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya bzlas pas /
NK010(tha)016:1228: mi dge ba rang rgyud du spyod pa'i rnam rtog bcom /
NK010(tha)016:1229: 'khor bar 'khyams kyi dogs pa'i blo dor /
NK010(tha)016:1230: myang 'das la chad par blta ba'i mtha' bsal nas
NK010(tha)016:1231: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i go 'phang
NK010(tha)016:1232: la bzhag pa'o // de ltar chags pa'i rten brgyad
NK010(tha)016:1233: dang steng 'og gnyis su bsgral ba rgyu'i las gtso
NK010(tha)016:1234: bor byas pas lus chags pa'i rgyu 'byung ba lnga
NK010(tha)016:1235: bcom pas rnam smin 'dus pa'i lus rten mi 'grub
NK010(tha)016:1236: la bzhag pa'o // pa'i phyir ro // des dag bya nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK010(tha)016:1237: lam rgyud lnga'i rten cing 'brel 'byung gi rtsa ba
NK010(tha)016:1238: gcod pas thob bya 'bras bu'i rang bzhin rten ye
NK010(tha)016:1239: shes lnga dang brten pa sku lnga dbyer med kyi
NK010(tha)016:1240: bdag nyid mngon sum du byas pa las sangs rgyas
NK010(tha)016:1241: zhes tshig bla dwags su byas pa ste /
NK010(tha)016:1243: dang po srid par lus grub pa //
NK010(tha)016:1244: lte ba chags pa'i rten gyur pa //
NK010(tha)016:1245: dngos po gang gis chags pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:1246: lus kyi chags pa'i rten brgyad la //
NK010(tha)016:1247: dbyings kyi khro mo rnam pa brgyad //
NK010(tha)016:1248: chags pa 'joms pa'i phur pa gdab //
NK010(tha)016:1249: dge sdig las kyi cha mnyam pas //
NK010(tha)016:1250: spyi bo rkang mthil rab btab pas //
NK010(tha)016:1251: de ltar bsgral ba'i dgos pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:1252: lam lnga las kyi rgyud lnga yi //
NK010(tha)016:1255: de nas sgo ma bzhi'i mngags phur mtsho bzhi la gdab pa ni /
NK010(tha)016:1257: shar nas zhi ba'i phrin las mdzad //
NK010(tha)016:1258: skye ka'i mgo can dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1259: dgra bgegs kun gyi rus pa'i mtsho //
NK010(tha)016:1260: klad pa'i rgyas su k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)016:1261: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh bi
NK010(tha)016:1262: da ya bi da ya sarba big nan bam h+aum
NK010(tha)016:1263: phata / byams pa tshad med kyi ngo bo bya phur btab pas bardzusa skyes dag /
NK010(tha)016:1264: zhi ba'i phrin las mthar phyin no //
NK010(tha)016:1266: lho nas rgyas pa'i phrin las mdzad //
NK010(tha)016:1267: srin bya'i mgo can dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1268: dgra bgegs kun gyi dbugs kyi mtsho //
NK010(tha)016:1269: glo ba'i dkyil du k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)016:1272: snying rje tshad med kyi ngo bo gser phur btab pas drod gsher skyes dag /
NK010(tha)016:1273: rgyas pa'i phrin las mthar phyin no //
NK010(tha)016:1275: nub nas dbang gi phrin las mdzad //
NK010(tha)016:1276: khra yi mgo can dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1277: dgra bgegs kun gyi khrag gi mtsho //
NK010(tha)016:1278: mchin pa'i dkyil du k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)016:1279: su ru su ru pra su ru /
NK010(tha)016:1280: dga' ba chen po'i ngo bo zangs phur btab pas sgo nga las skyes pa dag /
NK010(tha)016:1281: dbang gi phrin las mthar phyin no //
NK010(tha)016:1283: byang nas drag po'i phrin las mdzad //
NK010(tha)016:1284: pu shud mgo can dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1285: dgra bgegs kun gyi sha yi mtsho //
NK010(tha)016:1286: mkha' ma gnyis la k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)016:1287: m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya /
NK010(tha)016:1288: btang snyoms tshad med kyi ngo bo lcags phur btab pas mngal skyes dag /
NK010(tha)016:1289: drag po'i phrin las mthar phyin pa ste /
NK010(tha)016:1290: klad pa dbugs dang phyin pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:1291: mkhal mar bcas pa'i lus gnad la //
NK010(tha)016:1293: mtsho bzhi nyon mongs rab dag nas //
NK010(tha)016:1294: dag pa'i mtsho ni rab dag ste //
NK010(tha)016:1295: chos kyi dbyings su rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)016:1297: de nas phur pa de dag btab bzhin pa nas las kyi lha'i sngags rgyas mnan pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)016:1299: lag pa gnyis sor mo bsnol te /
NK010(tha)016:1301: mthe chung gnyis ngos la sbyar ba brgyangs te /
NK010(tha)016:1303: kar+m+aa badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)016:1304: lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas la /
NK010(tha)016:1305: g.yas phyogs nas bskor la k+ai la ya'i mgo la lan gsum gtug go //
NK010(tha)016:1306: de nas phur pa slar mi dbyung zhing /
NK010(tha)016:1307: sus kyang ma phyin par slar mi byung /
NK010(tha)016:1308: lhag par yang ma phyin par lhag par yang zung zhing /
NK010(tha)016:1311: de la phur pa thebs pa'i tshad ni /
NK010(tha)016:1312: bdag dang phur pa gzas po gsum //
NK010(tha)016:1313: gcig tu rtogs na thebs pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:1314: zhes pa'i don la 'byor bar bya'o //
NK010(tha)016:1315: zhar la gdab pa'i dus tshod la spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK010(tha)016:1317: dang por bsgrub par khas blangs nas //
NK010(tha)016:1318: ma thon bar du dus tshod min //
NK010(tha)016:1320: bzlas brjod nyin mtshan rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)016:1321: cho ga bzlas brjod tshang byas nas //
NK010(tha)016:1322: rab 'bring tha ma'i rtags rnams kun //
NK010(tha)016:1323: dus der mi 'byung mi srid do //
NK010(tha)016:1324: brdeg pa'i dus tshod rab mchog yin //
NK010(tha)016:1325: zhes pa las rab ni phur pa brdeg pa'am /
NK010(tha)016:1328: nyams pa khug dang ri dwags gsad //
NK010(tha)016:1329: bla shing gcad dang brag gshags dang //
NK010(tha)016:1330: sems can mang po gsad pa ste //
NK010(tha)016:1331: 'di ni kun la shes par bya //
NK010(tha)016:1333: phyi ma ni rtags dang rten 'brel gyi ngos nas dus sgrig pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)016:1334: rtags dang mtshan ma phyin pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:1335: brdeg pa'i dus la bab ces bya //
NK010(tha)016:1336: nam gyi gung dang nyi ma dros //
NK010(tha)016:1337: de la brdeg par rab tu shis //
NK010(tha)016:1339: gnam stong dang ni tshes brgyad dang //
NK010(tha)016:1340: bco lnga nyi shu gnyis la bya //
NK010(tha)016:1341: mig dmar phur bu gza' rnams drag /
NK010(tha)016:1342: brdeg pa'i dus la bab par bya //
NK010(tha)016:1344: de lta na'ang phur bu 'jig rten snang byed las
NK010(tha)016:1345: dbang phyug yab yum gyis skye 'gro srang la 'debs
NK010(tha)016:1346: shing bskul bas thebs pa'i dus dang de las ldog
NK010(tha)016:1349: dpyid ra ba'i bcu bzhi la thebs /
NK010(tha)016:1350: bcu bdun dang bcu dgu la ldog /
NK010(tha)016:1353: tha chung gi nyer gnyis la thebs /
NK010(tha)016:1355: dbyar ra ba'i brgyad la thebs /
NK010(tha)016:1359: tha chung bcu gcig las mi bya /
NK010(tha)016:1360: ston ra ba'i nyer gsum la thebs /
NK010(tha)016:1362: ston 'bring gi bcu bdun nas gnam stong bar thebs /
NK010(tha)016:1364: tha chung gi brgyad nas stong bar thebs //
NK010(tha)016:1366: dgun ra'i bcu gsum nas bcu drug bar thebs /
NK010(tha)016:1368: 'bring po'i nyer gnyis nas stong bar thebs /
NK010(tha)016:1370: tha chung gi nyer gnyis la thebs /
NK010(tha)016:1372: de ltar gdab phur nyi shu rtsa lngas rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad dang /
NK010(tha)016:1374: skye ba'i gnas rnam pa bzhi /
NK010(tha)016:1375: de dag gi nye ba len pa'i gnad gcod pas na /
NK010(tha)016:1376: gdab par bya ba'i phur pa ni /
NK010(tha)016:1377: nyi shu rtsa lngas rdzogs par byed //
NK010(tha)016:1379: rgyu gang gis zhe na tshig don thams cad nges don 'ba' zhig la ston pa /
NK010(tha)016:1380: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyud las /
NK010(tha)016:1381: khrag 'thung gtso bo yab yum gnyis //
NK010(tha)016:1382: phrin las kun gyi mdzad pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:1383: gdab pa'i las la mi 'jug par //
NK010(tha)016:1384: rgyal po chen po'i tshul du gnas //
NK010(tha)016:1385: thabs kyi sprul pa mgo brnyan rnams //
NK010(tha)016:1386: phyogs bcur phor nya'i las rnams kyi //
NK010(tha)016:1387: 'gugs pa la sogs bka' sdod tshul //
NK010(tha)016:1388: sgrol byed rnam dag mi 'gyur bas //
NK010(tha)016:1389: yang sprul phra thabs phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:1390: gnas su gdab par ma bstan to //
NK010(tha)016:1392: de lta na'ang rgyud kha cig las phra thabs dang
NK010(tha)016:1393: dam can gyi mgyogs phur 'debs par bshad pa ni
NK010(tha)016:1394: gab pa'i sngags drug dang 'brel bar dam can rnams
NK010(tha)016:1395: kyi sgos sgrub la sogs dmigs bsal can la dgongs
NK010(tha)016:1396: pa ste / gal te sgrub phur dang gdab phur
NK010(tha)016:1397: so sor nas ma tshang ba'i dus kyang gdab phur
NK010(tha)016:1398: ni dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi bdag nyid sras phur
NK010(tha)016:1399: kho nas byed pa'i tshul sbas pa zab mo las
NK010(tha)016:1400: pa ste / / rdo rje gzhon nu khro bo bcu //
NK010(tha)016:1401: sgrub phur dngos grub nod pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:1402: phra men srung ma'i phur pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:1403: sangs rgyas rnams kyi pho nya yin //
NK010(tha)016:1404: des kyang gdab par bya ba min //
NK010(tha)016:1405: sku gsung thugs las byung ba yi //
NK010(tha)016:1406: sras mchog k+ai la ya gsum ni //
NK010(tha)016:1407: gdab pa'i phur pa dam pa ste //
NK010(tha)016:1408: zhes pas gzhan rnams las bsgral ba'i rnam dag mi
NK010(tha)016:1409: rdzogs pa bla ma'i man ngag la brten nas rig
NK010(tha)016:1410: par bya ste / de skad du /
NK010(tha)016:1411: rgyud dkrugs lung gcus bye brag rnams //
NK010(tha)016:1412: bla ma'i thugs la rag las pas //
NK010(tha)016:1413: bla ma mnyes na rin chen rnyed //
NK010(tha)016:1414: ras chod can la rgyud lung gcus //
NK010(tha)016:1416: gsod pa'i thabs la rngon pa mkhas //
NK010(tha)016:1417: mngon spyod kun la yod mod de //
NK010(tha)016:1418: sngags kyi sgrol ba tshad phyin pa //
NK010(tha)016:1419: phur pa'i rgyud sde kho nar mthong //
NK010(tha)016:1420: rjes la gso ba gsum gyi las mi shes na /
NK010(tha)016:1421: dngos grub kyi nus pa nyams par byed pas /
NK010(tha)016:1422: thog mar phur pa gso ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:1424: b+ha ga'i thig le drangs nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:1425: chu srid kha ru thim par bsam //
NK010(tha)016:1426: b+ha ga rgyun gyi thig le dag /
NK010(tha)016:1427: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor steng gnas pa'i //
NK010(tha)016:1428: thig le gzi brjid chen por gyur //
NK010(tha)016:1430: gzi brjid chen pos brtan par bzhugs /
NK010(tha)016:1431: phur pa gso ba'i mtshan nyid do //
NK010(tha)016:1432: zhes gdab yul rnam thar gsum ldan gyi yum mkhar
NK010(tha)016:1433: byang chub sems kyi phur bu lugs ldog chen por
NK010(tha)016:1434: gdab pas bsgral bya'i rnam shes skye ba med pa'i
NK010(tha)016:1435: dbyings su sbyor ba'i sbas don gyi mtshan nyid rig
NK010(tha)016:1436: par byas nas rnam pa tsam du phur pa bton
NK010(tha)016:1438: k+ai la bco brgyad nges pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:1439: khro bor gsal ba nyi zlar bcas //
NK010(tha)016:1440: thams cad phur pa'i rgyan gyur pa //
NK010(tha)016:1442: zhes pas thog mar sras mchog gi phur pa nya bo las phyung la /
NK010(tha)016:1443: snang srid thams cad rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku 'ba'
NK010(tha)016:1444: zhig tu gsal ba'i rgyan du nyi zla gza' skar
NK010(tha)016:1445: 'od bkrag tu 'tsher ba de yang 'od du zhu
NK010(tha)016:1446: nas bsnyen phur la thim pas sngar bas gzi byin
NK010(tha)016:1447: mchog tu 'bar bar bsam la rtsa sngags brgya rtsa
NK010(tha)016:1448: brgyad bzla zhing phur pa klad la lan gsum bskor
NK010(tha)016:1449: ro // bar du bsgral ba rang brgyud la spang phyir thugs rjes bsgral bya gso ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:1450: pad+ma'i thig le drangs nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:1451: bsgrub bya'i lte ba'i dbus su bsnun //
NK010(tha)016:1452: bsgrub bya gso ba'i mtshan nyid do //
NK010(tha)016:1453: zhes pa'i don la'ang mtshon pa tsam du las thams
NK010(tha)016:1454: cad pa'i phur pa dkar nag mtshams su dril zhing
NK010(tha)016:1455: / k+ai la ya lan bco brgyad bzlas pa'i phur
NK010(tha)016:1456: pa las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis dmigs bya'i khams
NK010(tha)016:1457: bco brgyad sred len skad cig la bsregs nas /
NK010(tha)016:1458: h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes brjod pas rnam shes kyi ngo bo yi ge gsum du bsdus /
NK010(tha)016:1460: ces brjod pas de yang 'og min du dpal chen
NK010(tha)016:1461: yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams su 'phangs pas gzas pa
NK010(tha)016:1462: po rdo rje gzhon nu'i mtshan dpe'i ngo bo nyid
NK010(tha)016:1463: du sangs rgyas par bsam pa ste /
NK010(tha)016:1464: de ltar gnas gsum spar ba yis //
NK010(tha)016:1465: kho yang mi 'pham rgyal ngo shes //
NK010(tha)016:1467: tha mal mngon spyod kyi dgongs pa mthar phyin pa'i
NK010(tha)016:1468: don du bdag nyid kyi nus pa gso ba ni
NK010(tha)016:1469: / nyon cig lha mo rin chen ma //
NK010(tha)016:1470: dbus kyi thig le drangs nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:1471: 'bar ba'i dbyings su thim pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:1472: ro myong bde ba'i gzugs can nyid //
NK010(tha)016:1473: bdag nyid gso bar gsungs pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:1474: zhes bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la
NK010(tha)016:1475: brten nas rang gi ngo bo nyid du gso ba
NK010(tha)016:1476: nyid kyang / phyi don du gzas pa po'i lus kyi stobs dang /
NK010(tha)016:1478: ngag gi nus pa thams cad bdag la thim pas
NK010(tha)016:1479: bdag nyid gzi byin mchog tu 'bar bar bsam pa'i
NK010(tha)016:1480: tshul / byang chub rnam gsum bdag bstims pas //
NK010(tha)016:1481: bdag nyid bkrag mdangs bskyed pa ste //
NK010(tha)016:1482: sngags bcas bdag nyid gso ba'o //
NK010(tha)016:1483: zhes pas k+ai la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
NK010(tha)016:1484: h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bazla'o //
NK010(tha)016:1485: de ltar gso ba gsum gyi mtshan nyid shes na
NK010(tha)016:1486: chos nyid la rang bzhin med par rtogs pas zhe
NK010(tha)016:1488: ma rig pa'i gzhan dbang gis rnam pa thams cad
NK010(tha)016:1489: du ngan song gi rgyur gyur pa'i dmigs bya la
NK010(tha)016:1490: gzhi snying rjes gzung ste thabs la mkhas pa'i bsgral
NK010(tha)016:1491: bas bdag la rnam smin gyis mi gos /
NK010(tha)016:1492: pha rol po'ang rab chos nyid rtogs pa rnams kyis 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi rtsa ba 'byin /
NK010(tha)016:1493: 'bring dngos grub kyi mtshan ma mthong bas las ngan
NK010(tha)016:1494: gyi rten dang phral bas phyi rten bzang po la
NK010(tha)016:1495: sbyor / tha mas kyang sngags rgya ting nge 'dzin
NK010(tha)016:1496: gyi sgo nas las ngan gyi rgyud gcod pas sngags
NK010(tha)016:1497: kyi lam du drag shul gyi sbyor ba la bsgral
NK010(tha)016:1498: ba'i dam pa zhes gsungs te /
NK010(tha)016:1499: bsgral ba snying rje'i dbang gis te //
NK010(tha)016:1500: sems kyis sku ru rab bsgyur nas //
NK010(tha)016:1501: byang chub sems kyi bsgral bas te //
NK010(tha)016:1502: 'di ni bsgral ba'i dam pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:1504: gsum pa bsgral ba'i phung po lhag ma la sgrol byed mtshon chas dum bur bya ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:1505: dpal chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang las gdab
NK010(tha)016:1506: phur nyi shu rtsa bzhi po gzir bzhin pa la
NK010(tha)016:1507: / gsad gris nya bo gtub cing /
NK010(tha)016:1509: zhing bcu bsgral ba'i phung po la //
NK010(tha)016:1510: pho nya rol pa'i las bya yis //
NK010(tha)016:1511: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1512: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)016:1513: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK010(tha)016:1514: stobs chen khro bo chen po las //
NK010(tha)016:1515: mtshon chen sngon po 'bar ba yis //
NK010(tha)016:1516: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK010(tha)016:1517: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK010(tha)016:1518: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK010(tha)016:1520: las byed pho nya'i tshogs kyis mtshon cha 'khor lo dang /
NK010(tha)016:1525: rtse gsum la sogs pa'i char phab pas lus dum bu stong du 'thor bar bsams la /
NK010(tha)016:1526: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ma th+aa ma th+aa badz+ra /
NK010(tha)016:1530: sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:1531: de nas phur bu rnams bton la mdun du phur gdan la bzhugs su gsol /
NK010(tha)016:1532: bzhi pa phung po mthar byed thun dbab pa'i las ni /
NK010(tha)016:1547: phag khrag la sogs pa'i khrag thun sna tshogs dbab cing /
NK010(tha)016:1549: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)016:1550: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1551: sngon chad ji ltar dam bcas bzhin //
NK010(tha)016:1552: phyi rabs rnal 'byor phrin las dang //
NK010(tha)016:1553: bstan par dgra 'dre byung ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)016:1554: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1555: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1556: sa bdag chen mo dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1557: dregs pa mang po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1558: khyod kyi mthu rtsal rab tu dbyung //
NK010(tha)016:1559: sangs rgyas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:1560: dkon mchog sku dgra dben rtsa 'joms //
NK010(tha)016:1561: chos khrims 'dral dang slob dpon dgra //
NK010(tha)016:1563: bsad dang dbab dang nad ngan gyis //
NK010(tha)016:1564: ji nas brlag par khyod kyis gyis //
NK010(tha)016:1565: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ka tam ka te /
NK010(tha)016:1566: dza ye ta bi dza ye ta /
NK010(tha)016:1569: ma ra s+yee na pra marta ni ye h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:1570: ma ma pa shi ku ru ma tam nya ka
NK010(tha)016:1571: ra i nan d+ha ti ma ma karma shi kram
NK010(tha)016:1572: ka ra ya sarba big nan bam h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:1573: ces brjod pas phung po lhag ma rnams kyang rul
NK010(tha)016:1574: myags byer nas rdul phra rab tu 'thor bar bsam
NK010(tha)016:1575: mo // lnga pa gtun du brdung ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:1576: shes rab rnams kyi gsang ba'i gtun khung du /
NK010(tha)016:1577: thabs mchog rnams kyi rig pa ye shes kyi rdo
NK010(tha)016:1578: rje tho bas gzas pa po'i bag chags dang dngos
NK010(tha)016:1579: por 'dzin pa'i rnam rtog thams cad phye mar 'thag
NK010(tha)016:1580: pa'i byed las kyis phung po'i zag pa dngos med
NK010(tha)016:1581: bde stong chen po'i chos nyid du rtogs pa'i sbyor
NK010(tha)016:1582: sgrol zung 'jug gi don rtogs par byas nas /
NK010(tha)016:1584: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK010(tha)016:1585: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK010(tha)016:1586: rdo rje me dbal snying sreg nas //
NK010(tha)016:1587: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du lhogs //
NK010(tha)016:1588: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK010(tha)016:1589: rdo rje tho bas brdung byas nas //
NK010(tha)016:1590: lha yang rung ste brlag par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)016:1592: nyi shu rtsa gcig brjod pa dang de'i phyag rgya bcing ba spel lo //
NK010(tha)016:1593: drug pa zhal du bstab pa ni /
NK010(tha)016:1594: snod bcud kyi dngos po thams cad dpal chen rdo
NK010(tha)016:1595: rje gzhon nu'i sku che zhing yan lag rags pa
NK010(tha)016:1596: gdug pa can zil gyis gnon pa'i rgyan bkod kyi
NK010(tha)016:1597: che ba dang / gsung 'jigs pa'i sgra dbyangs kyis
NK010(tha)016:1598: ri rab kyang thal bar rlog pa'i gad rgyangs kyis
NK010(tha)016:1599: che ba dang / che ba dang / thugs zhi
NK010(tha)016:1600: ba chen po las ma g.yos bzhin du drag shul
NK010(tha)016:1601: khro gtum 'bar bas dmigs bya tshar gcod pa la
NK010(tha)016:1602: dpa' zhing rngam pa'i zhal du zhing bcu'i dgra bgegs
NK010(tha)016:1603: kyi sha khrag kha rje dbang thang dang bcas pa
NK010(tha)016:1606: bdag nyid chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1607: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)016:1608: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)016:1609: bsgo ba'i bka' ni nyan par byos //
NK010(tha)016:1612: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)016:1615: dam can spyi dril la stob pa /
NK010(tha)016:1616: shu shu tshal pa ni thum thum /
NK010(tha)016:1617: a n+ri tri ma ra sna /
NK010(tha)016:1619: n+aa ga rak+sha m+aa ra ya thum tshal pa thum ril kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)016:1622: gsang sngags kyi byin rlabs so //
NK010(tha)016:1624: a b+hi tsar+ya'i dus la bab bo //
NK010(tha)016:1625: brnag pa de kho na la'o //
NK010(tha)016:1626: zhes bden pa'i stobs kyi dmod pa dang /
NK010(tha)016:1628: h+aum gsum gyis dmigs bya la snying rje chen pos
NK010(tha)016:1629: kho'i brten pa sems kyi ngo bo thugs kyi sa
NK010(tha)016:1630: bon du bsdus / phata gsum gyis khro rgyal rnams
NK010(tha)016:1631: kyi ljags las 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu spros
NK010(tha)016:1632: pas rten rnam smin gyi phung po bkug nas rang
NK010(tha)016:1634: kh+aa hi'i mtha' can gyi sgras lhag ma med par gsol /
NK010(tha)016:1635: ha gsum gyis dgyes pa'i gad mo dang bcas bsgral
NK010(tha)016:1636: bya sgrol byed kyi gnyis 'dzin rang bzhin ma grub
NK010(tha)016:1637: pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag go //
NK010(tha)016:1638: de nas gdab phur nyer bzhi gso ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:1639: phur pa so so'i mtshan byang dang mthun pa'i lha dngos su skad cig gis gsal la /
NK010(tha)016:1641: srid pa phur bur sgrub pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:1642: dbang dang dngos grub stsol ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:1643: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1644: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)016:1645: rtags dang mtshan ma bstan pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:1646: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1647: zhes pas ye shes pa spyan drangs la bstim /
NK010(tha)016:1648: +aahh+aum gis sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlobs /
NK010(tha)016:1650: zhes pas rigs lnga'i rang bzhin du dbang bskur /
NK010(tha)016:1652: thabs kyi spyod pas gzhan don du //
NK010(tha)016:1653: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)016:1654: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)016:1655: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsal to //
NK010(tha)016:1656: sh+lo lo kas nges shes bskyed /
NK010(tha)016:1657: byug bdug brab gsum byas la lha gnas su dgod
NK010(tha)016:1658: pa yan chad ni thun gcig gi nges pa ste
NK010(tha)016:1659: / de lta bus thun bzhir ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa'i tshul ni /
NK010(tha)016:1660: rtsa ba dkyus ltar bshad kyang dkyus khong khrar btang
NK010(tha)016:1661: ba ste phur tshad la ma grags pa'i man ngag
NK010(tha)016:1662: khyad par can yin pa'i tshul /
NK010(tha)016:1663: sngags drug khong khrar gtang ba la //
NK010(tha)016:1664: las drug kun gyi mgo la sbyar //
NK010(tha)016:1665: las drug kun gyi zhabs la gdags //
NK010(tha)016:1666: lnga pa khong khrar gtang ba'i las //
NK010(tha)016:1667: dang po lha dang phral ba nas //
NK010(tha)016:1668: las bzhi kun gyi mgo la gdon //
NK010(tha)016:1669: drug tshan drug gi sngon 'gro yin //
NK010(tha)016:1670: las drug kun gyi rjes su sbyar //
NK010(tha)016:1671: zhabs su gdags pa'i man ngag yin //
NK010(tha)016:1672: lnga pa khong khrar gtang ba ni //
NK010(tha)016:1673: gdab las rdzogs pa'i dngos gzhi yin //
NK010(tha)016:1674: dang po nas bzung drug pa'i bar //
NK010(tha)016:1675: thun bzhir sbyor ba'i rim pa las //
NK010(tha)016:1676: drag po'i las drug rab tu 'bad //
NK010(tha)016:1677: de nas so so'i gsang sngags la //
NK010(tha)016:1678: shin tu gsang sngags de bzlas so //
NK010(tha)016:1679: zhes pa'i man ngag 'di bstan pa phyi dar gyi sgang nas slong shes pa tsam mi snang ngo //
NK010(tha)016:1680: de ltar shes na gtun du brdung ba'i snga rol pa /
NK010(tha)016:1681: las bzhi po'i phyi rol pa ste lnga par 'ong
NK010(tha)016:1682: ba de phur bu'i gdab las kyi khong khrar gtang
NK010(tha)016:1683: bas / zhag drug gis las la phur pa'i gdab las drug brgya 'byung ste /
NK010(tha)016:1685: mtshon cha'i dbal ni bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:1686: byug bdug brdeg pa yang yang bya //
NK010(tha)016:1687: phung po lnga la brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK010(tha)016:1688: khams dang skye mched de bzhin te //
NK010(tha)016:1693: brdung ba gsum so so nas nyi shu rtsa bzhis
NK010(tha)016:1694: ngan sngags kyi gzhung srong ba rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi
NK010(tha)016:1695: dgongs pa thun mong ma yin pa'i tshul le'u bcu
NK010(tha)016:1696: pa las / dgongs pa ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK010(tha)016:1697: nyin mtshan bcu gnyis dus dag la //
NK010(tha)016:1698: brgya drug phur pa'i gdab las kyis //
NK010(tha)016:1699: gsad pa yongs su rdzogs pa yin //
NK010(tha)016:1700: phrin las kun gyi gtso bo nyid //
NK010(tha)016:1701: gsang chen rmad du byung ba la //
NK010(tha)016:1702: 'jigs par byed pa'i skye bo gang //
NK010(tha)016:1703: drag po'i las kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK010(tha)016:1704: gzugs la mtshon gyis gtub bya zhing //
NK010(tha)016:1705: phung po mtha' byed thun gyi las //
NK010(tha)016:1706: rnam par sgrol ba sbyong ba'i thabs //
NK010(tha)016:1707: yab yum 'khril sbyor dgyes pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:1708: phung po bde chen dbyings su grol //
NK010(tha)016:1709: rang bzhin ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)016:1710: rnam par sbyong byed rdo rje nyid //
NK010(tha)016:1711: bsgral bas bde ba chen por 'grub //
NK010(tha)016:1713: de lta bu'i bsad las kyi cho ga rdzogs pas
NK010(tha)016:1714: ni rdo rje'i sku thob pa yang 'jig par byed
NK010(tha)016:1715: na / zhing bcu la sogs pa'i dgra bgegs rnams ni smos ci dgos te /
NK010(tha)016:1716: cho ga las kyi mthar byas pa //
NK010(tha)016:1717: brnag pa las kyi sbyor ba 'dis //
NK010(tha)016:1718: rdo rje'i sku yang rab 'jig na //
NK010(tha)016:1719: skye 'gro gzugs can smos ci dgos //
NK010(tha)016:1721: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la gnyis /
NK010(tha)016:1723: las gsum gyis mjug sdud pa'o //
NK010(tha)016:1725: bsnyen pa rnam pa gsum mthar phyin nas dngos grub blang ba'i tshul gnyis las /
NK010(tha)016:1726: skabs 'dir bsgral ba gnas su dag pa'i tshul gyis
NK010(tha)016:1727: thog mar dgra bgegs gnyis las dngos grub kyi bcud
NK010(tha)016:1728: blang ba rtsa rgyud kyi dgongs pa yin te /
NK010(tha)016:1729: sgrub pa chen po thon gyur nas //
NK010(tha)016:1730: bdag gi nus pa bstan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:1731: dmigs nas phur pa gdab byed pa //
NK010(tha)016:1732: dngos grub la dbang rgyal por 'gyur //
NK010(tha)016:1734: nyin bdun pa la r+au pa gsar du bcas la /
NK010(tha)016:1735: ye shes kyi lha nyer bar bsnyen pa dang /
NK010(tha)016:1736: dam can nye bar bsnyen pa'i bzlas thabs sngon du btang nas /
NK010(tha)016:1737: drag po'i phrin las dus gcig la smin pa'i phyir
NK010(tha)016:1738: ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa sngags drug sur phug
NK010(tha)016:1739: tu bstan pa'i gdab las khong khra can cig car
NK010(tha)016:1740: du byas nas btab pa'i bar tshang bar byed pa
NK010(tha)016:1741: ni / spogs pa'i cho ga yang yin la /
NK010(tha)016:1742: bsgrub pa chen po yang yin /
NK010(tha)016:1743: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i las chog kyang yin no //
NK010(tha)016:1745: mtshan ma mthong ba'i sgrub pa pos //
NK010(tha)016:1746: dngos grub rdzas dang dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK010(tha)016:1747: lha rnams sku gsum rang bzhin gyis //
NK010(tha)016:1748: bdag la rab tu bstim gyur na //
NK010(tha)016:1749: dngos grub bcud kyi dam pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:1750: phyag rgya chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)016:1751: zhes pas bsgrub pa mthar phyin pa'i tshul gyis ye
NK010(tha)016:1752: shes kyi lha la dngos grub blang ba ni sgrub
NK010(tha)016:1753: pa po rnams rgyan gos bzang por bya /
NK010(tha)016:1754: tshogs dang gtor ma rgya chen pos tshe gal la
NK010(tha)016:1755: sogs pas sna drangs te dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams
NK010(tha)016:1758: zhal bu mtshan ldan rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK010(tha)016:1759: 'chi med tshe yi g.yung drung ci bsam 'grub //
NK010(tha)016:1760: 'dun pa rigs kyi dngos grub zad med gter //
NK010(tha)016:1761: bdud 'dul lha nye gegs zhi rab tu bzang //
NK010(tha)016:1762: nye ba nyid du bsam pa da re ran //
NK010(tha)016:1763: yang dag bden pa'i dngos grub dam pa 'di //
NK010(tha)016:1764: ci bsam 'grub cing re ba skong ba dang //
NK010(tha)016:1765: rig 'dzin sa la nges par phyin pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:1766: thogs pa med par ci bsam 'grub pa yi //
NK010(tha)016:1767: dngos grub dam pa de nyid stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1769: chos nyid nam mkha' bsam med brjod las 'das //
NK010(tha)016:1770: thams cad 'byung zhing re ba ma lus skong //
NK010(tha)016:1771: bskangs pa nyid nas rgyal ba'i dbyings su thim //
NK010(tha)016:1772: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1774: byin rlabs chen po nam mkha'i sprin dang 'dra //
NK010(tha)016:1775: bdud dang srin po 'dul phyir rgyal ba'i rigs su byung //
NK010(tha)016:1776: dbang bskur byin rlabs nus pa bsam mi khyab //
NK010(tha)016:1777: sras kyi dam pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1779: thabs dang shes rab bde ba chen po'i dbyings //
NK010(tha)016:1780: yab la chags shing gnyis su med pa'i yum //
NK010(tha)016:1781: don dam ngang la rigs kyi yum du bstan //
NK010(tha)016:1782: zad med gter gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1784: gdug pa 'dul phyir yab kyi thugs las sprul //
NK010(tha)016:1785: dregs pa'i 'khor rnams ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)016:1786: yab yum rgyun du 'dzin cing las rnams 'grub //
NK010(tha)016:1787: thogs med sgrol ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1789: sku la dus gsum skye 'chi med //
NK010(tha)016:1790: rdo rje tshe yi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1791: stong gsum ma lus rlabs kyis gcod //
NK010(tha)016:1792: 'phur ldan gshog pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1793: 'jig rten kun la dbang sgyur ba'i //
NK010(tha)016:1794: rdzu 'phrul stobs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1796: thogs med stobs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1797: zas nor gos kyi gter mdzod la //
NK010(tha)016:1798: longs spyod dpag med dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1799: zhing bcu'i dgra bgegs tshar gcod pa'i //
NK010(tha)016:1800: sgrol byed mthu yi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1801: dregs pa zil gyi gnon mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)016:1802: mi 'jigs dpa' bo'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1803: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs sbyong byed pa'i //
NK010(tha)016:1804: lam la 'god pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1805: phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab la //
NK010(tha)016:1806: mdzad pa rdzogs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1807: bsgrub pa'i rgyal po bla na med //
NK010(tha)016:1808: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1809: sems ni rang byung ye shes kyi //
NK010(tha)016:1810: rtogs pas lhun grub dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1813: w+aa k+ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:1814: a la la hoh a la la hoh a la
NK010(tha)016:1815: la hoh zhes brjod cing kun la 'brim kyang dkyil
NK010(tha)016:1816: 'khor du mi dbang ba la ni mi sbyin no
NK010(tha)016:1817: // de nas gtso phur blangs la /
NK010(tha)016:1819: dngos grub dam pa thugs mchog lha yi lha //
NK010(tha)016:1820: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK010(tha)016:1821: dur khrod rdzas la brten te bsgrubs lags na //
NK010(tha)016:1822: snang srid byams pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1823: ye shes lha ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)016:1824: dngos grub stsal dang gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK010(tha)016:1825: gdug pa chen po thabs kyis 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:1826: drag pos 'dren pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1828: chos nyid kun tu bzang mo'i byin rlabs las //
NK010(tha)016:1829: dregs pa 'dul phyir thugs rje'i byin rlabs 'byung //
NK010(tha)016:1830: bdud kyi rgyal po r+au dra btul ba ltar //
NK010(tha)016:1831: bdud rgyal dregs pa 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1833: bdud dpung bcom nas chos nyid don mthong bas //
NK010(tha)016:1834: bdud rgyal r+au dras chos nyid don rtogs nas //
NK010(tha)016:1835: thugs rje'i byin rlabs bdud la snang ba ltar //
NK010(tha)016:1836: nyon mongs dbyings su bsgral ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1838: gtso phur gnas gsum du gtug pa dang bcas /
NK010(tha)016:1842: de bzhin du sras mchog rnams blangs la /
NK010(tha)016:1844: rol pa chen po'i sras mchog rnam lnga yang //
NK010(tha)016:1845: zhing bcu stobs dang rab tu 'bral mdzad pas //
NK010(tha)016:1846: bdud rgyal r+au tra grogs dang bral ba bzhin //
NK010(tha)016:1847: zhing bcu stobs dang bral ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1848: bud+d+ha badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma k+ai la ya k+aa ya w+aa k+ka tsit+ta sarba sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:1849: khro bo bcu'i phur pa blangs la /
NK010(tha)016:1851: 'khor gyi gdug pa ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:1852: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor 'khor dang bcas //
NK010(tha)016:1853: phyogs skyong dregs pa rab tu btul ba ltar //
NK010(tha)016:1854: 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1855: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:1859: sprul pa stong khams rab tu bkang nas kyang //
NK010(tha)016:1860: 'dul ba'i dbang gis gang la ci 'dul ston //
NK010(tha)016:1861: rgyal bas stong gsum sprul pas bkang ba ltar //
NK010(tha)016:1862: sprul pa khams gsum 'gengs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1863: h+aum zhes lan bcu'i mthar k+aa ya sogs /
NK010(tha)016:1866: rol pa chen po'i byin rlabs cir yang snang //
NK010(tha)016:1867: 'dul thabs drag po bdud kyi chas 'dra yang //
NK010(tha)016:1868: snying rje byang chub sems las nyams pa med //
NK010(tha)016:1869: drag po byams pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)016:1870: dza zhes bcu'i mthar k+aa ya sogs /
NK010(tha)016:1873: thugs rje byams pas 'gro la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK010(tha)016:1874: la lar zhi dang la lar khro bor snang //
NK010(tha)016:1875: 'dul thabs drag pos 'gro ba 'dul lags na //
NK010(tha)016:1876: nyon mongs gnas su 'dren pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1877: dzahh+aum bam hoh k+aa y+aa sogs /
NK010(tha)016:1880: dpal gyi bka' nyan las la brtson pa mo //
NK010(tha)016:1881: 'jig rten dregs pa ma lus 'dul mdzad ma //
NK010(tha)016:1882: 'jig rten dbang du sdud pa'i las byas ltar //
NK010(tha)016:1883: dam las mi 'da' bka' nyan dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1887: 'jig rten khams la dbang sgyur mthu mo che //
NK010(tha)016:1888: las ngan zhing bcu ma lus sgrol mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)016:1889: bcol zhing rbad na pho nya mdzad pa ltar //
NK010(tha)016:1890: gang du mngags pa'i las 'grub dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1891: e yam ma ya k+aa ya sogs /
NK010(tha)016:1894: dregs pa sde bzhi rab tu 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)016:1895: nad kyi bdag mo bka' nyan gsung sdod ma //
NK010(tha)016:1896: bran dang pho nya las rnams 'grub byed ltar //
NK010(tha)016:1897: gang la bya ba'i las 'grub dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1898: b+h+yo bzhi'i mthar k+aa ya sogs dang /
NK010(tha)016:1900: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1901: don dam chos nyid rtogs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1902: sangs rgyas sa la 'gro ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1903: 'khor ba ngan song sbyong ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)016:1904: zhes brjod pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK010(tha)016:1905: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dngos grub thob
NK010(tha)016:1906: par bsam mo // de nas mngon spyod kyi phrin
NK010(tha)016:1907: las mthar phyin pa'i don du phur skor gyi gdab
NK010(tha)016:1908: par bsam mo // las ni / dzapa kha phye la /
NK010(tha)016:1909: bzlas pa stong phrag gcig byas rjes /
NK010(tha)016:1910: chu srin rnam rol gyi rgyas gtso phur blangs te dril nas /
NK010(tha)016:1911: mgo la g.yas skor du bskor bas rang gi lus
NK010(tha)016:1912: la bar du gcod pa thams cad kyi lus rdul
NK010(tha)016:1913: phra rab tu song bar bsam la /
NK010(tha)016:1915: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)016:1916: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)016:1918: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)016:1919: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par shog /
NK010(tha)016:1920: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:1923: yang mgrin par bskor bas pha rol pa'i ngag gi nus pa bcing /
NK010(tha)016:1924: rang gi nus pa rgyas par bsams la /
NK010(tha)016:1926: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)016:1927: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK010(tha)016:1928: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK010(tha)016:1929: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK010(tha)016:1930: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK010(tha)016:1931: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK010(tha)016:1932: badz+ra k+ai la k+ai la h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:1934: yang snying ga nas mdun rgyab tu bskor bas rang
NK010(tha)016:1935: gi sems la rnam par g.yengs pas bar du gcod
NK010(tha)016:1937: pha rol po'i sems skrag cing myos pa'i mod la
NK010(tha)016:1938: rig pa chos nyid kyi klong du brgyal bar bsams
NK010(tha)016:1940: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)016:1941: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK010(tha)016:1942: phur po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK010(tha)016:1943: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK010(tha)016:1944: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK010(tha)016:1946: de nas sgrub pa po thams cad kyis kyang dzapa
NK010(tha)016:1947: bzla bzhin par phur bskor byas rjes phur pa sa
NK010(tha)016:1948: la ma reg par nya bo'i khog pa la gzhug
NK010(tha)016:1949: / de bzhin du khro bcu yab yum dang /
NK010(tha)016:1950: sgo ma'i phur pa rnams kyang rdo rje slob dpon
NK010(tha)016:1951: nas rim par phur bskor byas nas dkyil 'khor la
NK010(tha)016:1953: tshogs kyi 'khor los dgyes pa bskang /
NK010(tha)016:1954: dam can chos skyong rnams la gtang rag dbul /
NK010(tha)016:1955: chad mdo nas bzung cho ga'i rjes chog rnams dkyus ltar bya'o //
NK010(tha)016:1956: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa ni /
NK010(tha)016:1958: las kyi mtha' brtul nges pa yang //
NK010(tha)016:1959: hom la bsreg pa'i sbyor ba yis //
NK010(tha)016:1960: rdo rje me dbal snying bsreg nas //
NK010(tha)016:1962: mnan sa nges par mnan pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:1964: zhes las kyi mtha' bsdu ba'i rim pa gsum las /
NK010(tha)016:1965: dang po bsad pa'i las mthar phyin pa'i de ma
NK010(tha)016:1966: thag bstab pa'i las kyis ma tshang ba kha skong
NK010(tha)016:1967: ba ni drag po'i sbyin sreg yin te /
NK010(tha)016:1969: gang dag bsad pa'i dum bu dang //
NK010(tha)016:1970: phung po snyoms pa'i rjes shun can //
NK010(tha)016:1971: sha khrag drod dang bcas pa la //
NK010(tha)016:1973: tsha ba'i mar dang lan tsh+wa dang //
NK010(tha)016:1974: ske tshe dug dang khrag sna dang //
NK010(tha)016:1975: lcags phye ldong ros dam rdzas dang //
NK010(tha)016:1976: sol phyes bgos pa'i dam rdzas rnams //
NK010(tha)016:1977: gsang sngags bzlas par rab 'bad de //
NK010(tha)016:1978: gang gi gzugs ming rus bsregs na //
NK010(tha)016:1980: zhes pas de'i tshul ni drag po'i sbyin sreg rta
NK010(tha)016:1981: gdong rngam zhugs las rtogs par bya zhing rdzas la
NK010(tha)016:1984: der dug pa can gyi shing rnams la kha ral ma'i skras bcings te /
NK010(tha)016:1985: dug shing sna tshogs pa la snying dang glo bas brgyan pa ni drag po me'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK010(tha)016:1987: bstab pa'i dkyil 'khor ni byang shar mtshams su 'phang
NK010(tha)016:1988: du sor bzhi la snying po n+ri tri dang bcas
NK010(tha)016:1989: pa'o // der bsgral ba'i ling+ga ni ra sog dang /
NK010(tha)016:1991: mi'i sog pa la bris la mchod pa chen po'i dus su bstab bo //
NK010(tha)016:1993: dam can spyi 'dril gyi bsreg sngags /
NK010(tha)016:1995: d+hi dzahni yo g+ai shwa ri ni ya ma tsit+ta
NK010(tha)016:1996: su tri badz+ra m+aa ra ya phatahram ram kh+aa hi
NK010(tha)016:1997: ho hoh zhes pa dkyil 'khor pa'i mjug tu sbyar
NK010(tha)016:1998: nas lan lnga tsam dbul lo //
NK010(tha)016:1999: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sbyor ba yis //
