NK010(tha)016:2000: dum bur gtub nas sbyin bsreg bya //
NK010(tha)016:2001: thal ba rgya mtshor dor gyur na //
NK010(tha)016:2002: nges pa kho nar smyo bar 'gyur //
NK010(tha)016:2003: khyi yi khrag dang rnga mo'i sha /
NK010(tha)016:2004: dug gi me la bsreg gyur na //
NK010(tha)016:2005: nges pa kho nar khug par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)016:2006: tsit+ta'i khrag dang dur khrod sa //
NK010(tha)016:2007: shwa na rak+ta bsres pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:2008: gzugs brnyan sor ni bzhi pa byas //
NK010(tha)016:2009: b+han+d+ha srubs med nang du gzhug /
NK010(tha)016:2010: ma ki ta yi khu bas byug /
NK010(tha)016:2011: dur khrod shing la bsreg gyur na //
NK010(tha)016:2012: bsgrub bya tsha ba'i rims kyis 'debs //
NK010(tha)016:2013: dur khrod dag gi sol ba la //
NK010(tha)016:2014: bsgrub bya'i gzugs brnyan nag por bya //
NK010(tha)016:2015: ra yi khrag gis byug nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:2016: dur khrod shing gi me la bsreg /
NK010(tha)016:2017: na ra'i phur pa lnga pos bdug /
NK010(tha)016:2018: hi hir bzhad cing thal brdabs pas //
NK010(tha)016:2022: mi sha khyi sha ra dang rta //
NK010(tha)016:2023: n+ri dang gnyis su med bsreg na //
NK010(tha)016:2026: mi rta khyi spyang glang dred tshil gyis gag pa /
NK010(tha)016:2027: mi khyi 'phar spyang spre'u ra dang bcas pa'i khrag nad /
NK010(tha)016:2028: de dag gi rkang mar gyis tshad rims /
NK010(tha)016:2029: ra spyang bong dug bse zho dang bcas pas lkugs /
NK010(tha)016:2030: li khri dang mtshal gyis skye rgyun gcod /
NK010(tha)016:2031: gu gul dang nyung kar gyis lha dang 'bral /
NK010(tha)016:2032: thang phrom dang lug mig pas smyo 'bog /
NK010(tha)016:2033: nyung dkar nag ske tshe til gyis snying gas /
NK010(tha)016:2037: sman chen gyi kun gyi grogs /
NK010(tha)016:2038: gta' gtor rnying pas btab pa'i rdzas de rnam pa bcu drug bshad pa'ang man ngag tu sbyar ro //
NK010(tha)016:2039: gnyis pa gsad pa'i las chud mi za ba zor gyi las kyis byed de /
NK010(tha)016:2040: de'i tshul ni zor las gnam lcags 'bar ba las
NK010(tha)016:2041: rtogs par bya zhing zor rdzas la man ngag tu
NK010(tha)016:2042: bstan pa ni / nyung dkar nyung nag ske tshe mtshe //
NK010(tha)016:2043: mche ba can gyi mchu dgu khrag /
NK010(tha)016:2044: thun du brabs te zor 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2046: nyung dkar nyung nag skye tshe mtshe //
NK010(tha)016:2047: mdze pho'i khrag zor thun 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2049: nyung dkar la sogs mi ra khyi //
NK010(tha)016:2050: sna tshogs dug dang khrag thun gyis //
NK010(tha)016:2051: khyim mam yul phyogs zor 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2052: myos dang barlamasa dang lkugs dang 'chi //
NK010(tha)016:2053: nyung kar la sogs mi ra khyi //
NK010(tha)016:2054: d+ha du ra yi lug mig dang //
NK010(tha)016:2055: sna tshogs dug dang khrag thun gyis //
NK010(tha)016:2056: khyim mam yul phyogs zor 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2058: 'brum nad dag gis shi ba'i khrag /
NK010(tha)016:2059: nyung kar dug dang sbyar ba yis //
NK010(tha)016:2060: khyim mam yul phyogs zor 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2062: mkhris nad rtsa yi khrag dang ni //
NK010(tha)016:2063: nyung dkar nyung nag dug sna tshogs //
NK010(tha)016:2064: khyim mam yul phyogs zor 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2066: nyung dkar nyung nag ske tshe mtshe //
NK010(tha)016:2067: mu zi nag po khrag sna tshogs //
NK010(tha)016:2068: khyim mam yul phyogs zor 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2069: pho log glang thabs nad kyis 'chi //
NK010(tha)016:2070: smyos rims rtsa yi khrag dang ni //
NK010(tha)016:2071: nyung kar la sogs dug sna tshogs //
NK010(tha)016:2072: khyim mam yul phyogs zor 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2074: yul mkhar sa dang tshon phye dang //
NK010(tha)016:2075: lo zlar bshams pa'i gtor ma dang //
NK010(tha)016:2076: nyung kar la sogs dme khrag gis //
NK010(tha)016:2077: khyim mam yul phyogs zor 'phangs na //
NK010(tha)016:2080: dregs pa'i las sbyor dang 'brel ba'i thod zor bye brag pa'i man ngag ni /
NK010(tha)016:2081: nag po spyi dkar thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)016:2082: de nyid snying dang khrag tu bcas //
NK010(tha)016:2083: mon pa nag po'i snying yang rung //
NK010(tha)016:2084: de yi nang du ming byang gzhug /
NK010(tha)016:2085: re ba'i khug mar bcug kyang rung //
NK010(tha)016:2086: gsal ba lha yi nga rgyal gyis //
NK010(tha)016:2087: gang yin dmigs pa gsal ba las //
NK010(tha)016:2088: dkar nag mtshams su drag sngags brdeg /
NK010(tha)016:2089: de yis rtags la las sngags bya //
NK010(tha)016:2090: grangs su bstan pa'i las nyid de //
NK010(tha)016:2092: dkar po phrum dmar thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)016:2093: snying sna lnga yang de bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)016:2094: ming dang rus kyang bri bar bya //
NK010(tha)016:2095: thun rdzas sna tshogs mang du bstar //
NK010(tha)016:2096: gsal ba'i ting 'dzin dgongs pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:2097: rang bsrung gnad la dbab par bya //
NK010(tha)016:2098: thun rnams dus su brab par bya //
NK010(tha)016:2099: rtags ni myur du byung ba dang //
NK010(tha)016:2100: gang yin de la thod pa brdeg /
NK010(tha)016:2101: de ni sa ru rtags byung na //
NK010(tha)016:2102: bsams pa'i 'bras bu chud mi za //
NK010(tha)016:2103: gang byas las la the tshom med //
NK010(tha)016:2104: mon pa nag po'i thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)016:2105: gla ba lug dang bya rnams kyi //
NK010(tha)016:2106: snying dang khrag tu bcas pa blug /
NK010(tha)016:2107: dam rdzas kun kyang tshang gyur na //
NK010(tha)016:2109: rim pa sngags kyi bya bar shes //
NK010(tha)016:2111: wa'am spyang ki'i thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)016:2112: rims kyis shi ba'i khrag blug la //
NK010(tha)016:2113: dug dang sbang ma slang bar bya //
NK010(tha)016:2114: zangs phye dug rnams yang dag bstan //
NK010(tha)016:2115: sbyor ba sngags kyi na ya la //
NK010(tha)016:2116: gnad la dbab par rab sdebs la //
NK010(tha)016:2117: nam gyi 'jing la thun yang brdeg /
NK010(tha)016:2118: rtags rnams 'byung bar gdon mi za //
NK010(tha)016:2119: khams gsum gdug pa sgrol ba'i las //
NK010(tha)016:2120: gang du btab pa 'grub par byed //
NK010(tha)016:2121: bdud dang srin po gnod sbyin yang //
NK010(tha)016:2124: 'di dam can gyi gnad yig lam brten par rang
NK010(tha)016:2125: gar byas na rang nyid phung bas bshad rgyud le'u
NK010(tha)016:2126: nyi shu pa dang nyer gcig pa ltar 'bod rbad
NK010(tha)016:2127: bsad gsum la brten pa gces shing /
NK010(tha)016:2129: zhes pa'i don yang rig par bya'o //
NK010(tha)016:2130: 'dir sbyin sreg gi thal ba rlung la bskur ba zor ni /
NK010(tha)016:2132: mtshan ngan gyi thod pa bla 'og ma bral ba dang /
NK010(tha)016:2133: me chus nus pa ma gsad pa'i zhog glang 'og can la sogs pa'i rwar bsregs thal /
NK010(tha)016:2136: yugs sa'i mnga' khrag sogs blug /
NK010(tha)016:2137: thun rdzas gzhan rnams dang zor rdzas rnams ni thal
NK010(tha)016:2138: sol la zor kong dang gtor ma byas pa la
NK010(tha)016:2139: brgyan / ma dal gru gsum can gyi steng du bkod /
NK010(tha)016:2140: de'i mdun du sman gtor rak+ta mchod pa dang bcas pa bsham /
NK010(tha)016:2141: dkyil 'khor gzhung ltar bskyed la dzapa bzlas rdzogs nas
NK010(tha)016:2142: ma ma pa shi ku ru sogs ci nus bzla
NK010(tha)016:2143: / phur pa'i dam can gyi bskul bya /
NK010(tha)016:2144: de nas nam phyed la bab pa na /
NK010(tha)016:2145: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK010(tha)016:2146: srid pa spyi blugs kyi zhwa sogs bdud chas su zhugs /
NK010(tha)016:2147: snying gar zhag gi zo ris /
NK010(tha)016:2148: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK010(tha)016:2149: mkhur tshos dang lkog ma rnams rak+ta'i thig le bya /
NK010(tha)016:2150: gtor ma bzang po gsum bcas la gcig rang gi chos skyong la phul nas las la bskul /
NK010(tha)016:2151: gcig phyogs skyong rnams la phul la bden pa bdar /
NK010(tha)016:2152: ma nyes pa'i yus kha gzug /
NK010(tha)016:2153: gcig pha rol pa'i gzhi bdag dang skyob byed la byin nas phyogs gzhan du bzur bar bsam /
NK010(tha)016:2154: de nas dam can gyi sngags dang zor sngags dmigs
NK010(tha)016:2155: pa ma yengs par bzla bzhin pas dgra yul mthong
NK010(tha)016:2156: ba'am / ri mthon po'i rtser phyogs la /
NK010(tha)016:2158: nga ni dpal chen khrag 'thung gtso //
NK010(tha)016:2160: dam can gyi zor sngags gab pa 'bu li 'bu li kham badz+ra shishaha&a&a&a ni ri sha ni /
NK010(tha)016:2161: khyi khri snying za tsit+ta yam pa to b+h+yo b+h+yo thun yam /
NK010(tha)016:2164: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)016:2165: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu la //
NK010(tha)016:2166: sogs kyi zor bskul dang sbrag /
NK010(tha)016:2167: rab dgra bo'i dur ma chad /
NK010(tha)016:2169: tha ma yul phyogs la 'phang na rim pa bzhin mdun rgyud dang /
NK010(tha)016:2172: gsum pa las mthar bya ba ni klu la gtad pa mnan pa'i las yin te /
NK010(tha)016:2175: phur byed sa la gzugs byas te //
NK010(tha)016:2176: dri chen po yis byug nas su //
NK010(tha)016:2177: ra ma ya yi dud pas bdug /
NK010(tha)016:2178: dur khrod ro yi shun lpags la //
NK010(tha)016:2179: 'khor lo bcu gcig rtsibs mchan bri //
NK010(tha)016:2180: dbus su bsgrub bya'i ming gis brgyan //
NK010(tha)016:2181: mthar ni ma h+aa sa yar ldan //
NK010(tha)016:2182: pho rog sgro yi myu gu yis //
NK010(tha)016:2183: gdug pa can gyi gzugs bris la //
NK010(tha)016:2184: b+han+d+ha kha sbyar nang du bcug /
NK010(tha)016:2185: khrag chen po yis byug par bya //
NK010(tha)016:2186: gzugs brnyan de yi snying gar gzhug /
NK010(tha)016:2187: tsan+dana me la dros par bsro //
NK010(tha)016:2188: lam chen rgya gram dag tu mnan //
NK010(tha)016:2189: zhes pas sbyin sreg gi thal ba dang ling ro
NK010(tha)016:2190: phung sa rnams bsres pa'i ling+ga'i khog par ming rus
NK010(tha)016:2192: phyi nang thams cad khrag chen gyis byug /
NK010(tha)016:2193: phyi thum ro shun nam nya lpags sam ro ras skyer shun nam ka ra bi ras byug /
NK010(tha)016:2194: ri rab kyi rtser rgya gram rwa gdengs dang lte
NK010(tha)016:2195: bar 'khor lo rtsibs bcu gcig par bris pa'i dbus
NK010(tha)016:2196: dang rtsibs rnams la bsgrub bya'i ming rus mthar zil
NK010(tha)016:2197: gnon gyi sngags / lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha nan /
NK010(tha)016:2200: rtsibs mchan la sdig pa bri /
NK010(tha)016:2201: mu khyud la ma tam nya ka ra dang /
NK010(tha)016:2202: sngags drug bris pas bstums pa'i tshe /
NK010(tha)016:2203: lam gyi sngags ye shes kyi ri rab rtse brgyad par bsam pa spyi bor bkab ste dril /
NK010(tha)016:2207: mdzo drel gang rung gi thod pa bla 'og kha phral ba'i nang du bcug /
NK010(tha)016:2208: khrag sna dug sna thun rdzas sogs kyang blugs nas kha sbyar /
NK010(tha)016:2209: dgug gzhug drag po byas la /
NK010(tha)016:2210: phung re dang tshon skud kyis bcings nas kha sbub la /
NK010(tha)016:2211: shu shu rak+sha tshal pa a be sha shu la kang keng m+aa ra ya phata /
NK010(tha)016:2214: de nas nam gyi smad cha la bab pa na gang du bya ba'i gnas ni /
NK010(tha)016:2215: ma mo'i gnas dang chu brag 'thab //
NK010(tha)016:2216: lam gyi gzhi mdo shing gcig drung //
NK010(tha)016:2217: klu gnas chu mig lkugs pa ru //
NK010(tha)016:2218: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i phur pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:2219: sngags bzlas gru gsum brkos nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:2220: zhes pa ltar dong gru gsum rgyar khru gang zabs su khru do pa brus la /
NK010(tha)016:2221: khrag sna dang ro sol gyis nag por bya /
NK010(tha)016:2222: dkar gtor dmar gtor gnyis bshams la /
NK010(tha)016:2223: dkar gtor gnas de'i gzhi bdag la bsngosa te mnyes pa'i dpang gzug /
NK010(tha)016:2224: dam bdar nas las kyi stong grogs bcol /
NK010(tha)016:2225: dmar gtor dam can rnams la phul nas phrin las bcol /
NK010(tha)016:2226: de'i nang du mnan thod kha mthur du sbub nas bcug /
NK010(tha)016:2227: phur pa rnams kyi spyi bo ru //
NK010(tha)016:2228: ri rab gling bzhi bris nas ni //
NK010(tha)016:2229: steng du don yod grub pa ni //
NK010(tha)016:2230: yi ge h+aa las bskyed byas te //
NK010(tha)016:2231: rtag tu brtan par bzhugs par bya //
NK010(tha)016:2233: bsregs pa'i thal ba la sogs pa thams cad mnan par bya ba ni /
NK010(tha)016:2234: las rnams ma grub bar du bzhag /
NK010(tha)016:2235: las rnams grub pa'i mod la ni /
NK010(tha)016:2236: myur du zhi ba'i thabs la 'bad //
NK010(tha)016:2237: ces pa ltar bsreg thal lhag ma ma lus par blug /
NK010(tha)016:2238: dgra la rtags byung nas mnan /
NK010(tha)016:2239: phur pa bton la khrus gsol dang /
NK010(tha)016:2240: mnan chas rnams la zhi ba'i sbyin sreg gam chu klung la sbyangs shing smon lam bzang po gdab /
NK010(tha)016:2241: rang rdo rje gzhon nur gsal /
NK010(tha)016:2242: sder mo 'byung ba'i sngags 'di brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas /
NK010(tha)016:2243: na mahs man+ta che ge mo'i k+aa ya w+aa k+ka tsit+ta badz+ra n+aan /
NK010(tha)016:2246: g+h+aa ta ya che ge mo sarba dush+t+aam phata /
NK010(tha)016:2247: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:2249: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)016:2250: badz+ra d+ha ra adz+ny+aa pa ya ti /
NK010(tha)016:2251: che ge mo'i k+aa ya w+aa k+ka tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:2252: ces bzlas pa'i mod la rdo rje rgya gram gyi
NK010(tha)016:2253: 'tshub ma phyogs kun nas langs te mnan thod kyi
NK010(tha)016:2254: steng du spungs la rdul phra rab tu 'thas pa'i
NK010(tha)016:2255: ri rab chen po lam gyis byung bar bsams la
NK010(tha)016:2256: dur g.yam steng du rgya gram bris pas kha gcad
NK010(tha)016:2257: / me chus bcad pa'i sa rim pa dgus mnan /
NK010(tha)016:2258: lam h+aum lam sum lam pra ti s+t+wam b+ha ya /
NK010(tha)016:2264: bdag nyid 'bar ba'i gar la sogs //
NK010(tha)016:2265: stangs stabs rdzogs nas bro brdung bya //
NK010(tha)016:2266: zhes pa'i khro bo'i stangs stabs dang bcas /
NK010(tha)016:2268: rdo rjee gzhon nu'i zhabs kyis mnan //
NK010(tha)016:2270: khro bo'i tshogs kyi zas su bsngo //
NK010(tha)016:2271: bskal pa'i me yi phung pos bsreg /
NK010(tha)016:2272: ye shes me yis bag chags bsreg /
NK010(tha)016:2273: nyon mongs lnga dang ldan pa yi //
NK010(tha)016:2274: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)016:2275: byang chub sems ni ma skyes bar //
NK010(tha)016:2276: nam yang btang bar mi bya'o //
NK010(tha)016:2278: lag pa lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas las bzhi so so'i bro ra dang bcas /
NK010(tha)016:2280: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK010(tha)016:2281: 'jig rten khams ni thams cad kun //
NK010(tha)016:2282: khro bor ma gyur gang yang med //
NK010(tha)016:2283: thams cad thal ba'i rdul du rlogs //
NK010(tha)016:2284: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:2288: dbang gi khro bor ma gyur med //
NK010(tha)016:2289: thams cad dbang du 'du bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)016:2290: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:2291: pa sham ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)016:2293: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK010(tha)016:2295: rgyas par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK010(tha)016:2296: tshe dang bsod nams 'phel bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)016:2297: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:2300: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK010(tha)016:2302: zhi bar ma gyur gang yang med //
NK010(tha)016:2303: thams cad ma lus zhi bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)016:2304: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)016:2306: nang du log nas tshe 'gugs dang /
NK010(tha)016:2307: shis pa brjod pas mtha' bsdu zhing re dogs med pa'i chos nyid la mnyam par 'jog par bya'o //
NK010(tha)016:2308: tshul de lta bus a b+hi tsar+ya'i phrin las mthar
NK010(tha)016:2309: phyin pa la sgrol ba tshad du 'khyol ba zhes
NK010(tha)016:2311: 'jig rten pha rol dag tu ni //
NK010(tha)016:2312: bsgral ba rnams kyang mtho ris thob //
NK010(tha)016:2313: bdag kyang byang chub gnyis su med //
NK010(tha)016:2314: bsam pa 'byor ba'i shes rab lags //
NK010(tha)016:2315: sdig can bsad na las ngan 'chad //
NK010(tha)016:2317: de bas na sngags kyi thabs la mkhas pa dang /
NK010(tha)016:2318: byang chub kyi sems khyad par can gyis zin pas rnam smin ngan pas mi gos shing /
NK010(tha)016:2319: zhing bcu tshar bcad pas bstan 'gro'i don chen po dang /
NK010(tha)016:2320: bdag nyid byang chub bsgrub pa'i 'gal rkyen zhi nas
NK010(tha)016:2321: phrin las bzhi dang mchog gi dngos grub thob pa'i
NK010(tha)016:2322: tshul / sangs rgyas kun gyi mdzad pa yi //
NK010(tha)016:2323: 'gro ba'i don du phrin las bzhi //
NK010(tha)016:2324: 'di ltar thogs pa med spyod pas //
NK010(tha)016:2325: dngos grub bar gcod tshar gcod sogs //
NK010(tha)016:2326: brtul zhugs can gyi rnal 'byor la //
NK010(tha)016:2327: shin tu 'grub par nga yis bstan //
NK010(tha)016:2328: yon tan phun sum tshogs grub pas //
NK010(tha)016:2329: rang byung ye shes rtogs par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)016:2330: 'khor dang longs spyod kun rgyas shing //
NK010(tha)016:2331: bkra shis dpal ni yongs rdzogs byed //
NK010(tha)016:2333: dbyings la bdud rtsi dri med zab //
NK010(tha)016:2335: rgyud kyi khong snying bton pa 'di //
NK010(tha)016:2336: pad+ma'i lung bstan thob las byung //
NK010(tha)016:2337: 'di la bcos bslad byed pa dang //
NK010(tha)016:2338: gdams ngag btus nas khungs bzang por //
NK010(tha)016:2339: 'chos pa byung na de'i don snying //
NK010(tha)016:2340: shwa na mched bzhi'i zhal du rol //
NK010(tha)016:2341: rgyal bstan spyi dang bye brag tu //
NK010(tha)016:2342: snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa yis //
NK010(tha)016:2344: de 'dra'i srog gi spu grir rgya //
NK010(tha)016:2345: slob dpon chen po pad+ma'i zhabs kyi jo mo rdo
NK010(tha)016:2346: rje 'jigs byed nyi ma dbang phyug rtsal la gdams
NK010(tha)016:2347: pa'i man ngag lag lhag rdo rje byang chub slob
NK010(tha)016:2348: mar bcas pa'i bar du bka' nas bkar brgyud pa'i
NK010(tha)016:2350: rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho lta bu'i
NK010(tha)016:2351: bcud phyung ba 'di nyid 'dri ba'i dbu brtsams pa
NK010(tha)016:2352: nas ma grub bar du 'tshubs lhangs kyang bltar mngon
NK010(tha)016:2353: pa rgyun chags su byung zhing /
NK010(tha)016:2354: grub 'bras kyang bslu med du mthong ba yin pas kun la mi ston pa'i bka' rgya yod do //
